1990年代后期，凯莉开始筹备其他项目<ref name="shapiro21">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=114}}</ref>。1998年4月14日，凯莉参与{{tsl|en|VH1 Divas|VH1 Divas}}{{tsl|en|benefit concert|慈善演唱会}}，和[[艾瑞莎·弗蘭克林|艾瑞莎·弗蘭克林]]、[[席琳·狄翁|席琳·狄翁]]、[[仙妮亞·唐恩|仙妮亞·唐恩]]、[[格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡|格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡]]和[[卡洛爾·金|卡洛爾·金]]同台献唱<ref name=divas>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/28692993.html?dids=28692993:28692993&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Apr+16%2C+1998&author=Bruce+Haring&pub=USA+TODAY&desc=VH1+display+of+'Divas'+makes+all+feel+'Natural'&pqatl=google|title=VH! Display of Divas Makes Me Feel 'Natural'|last=Haring|first=Bruce|work=USA Today|date=1998-04-16|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725032117/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/28692993.html?dids=28692993%3A28692993&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AFT&type=current&date=Apr+16%2C+1998&author=Bruce+Haring&pub=USA+TODAY&desc=VH1+display+of+%27Divas%27+makes+all+feel+%27Natural%27&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-25}}</ref>。凯莉筹备电影作品《All That Glitters》，后将其改名为《[[星梦泪痕_(2001年电影)|星梦泪痕]]》<ref name=boston>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/bostonherald/access/80313960.html?dids=80313960:80313960&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Sep+11%2C+2001&author=SARAH+RODMAN&pub=Boston+Herald&desc=Music%3B+All+that+litters+`Glitter'%3B+Carey+displays+newfound+maturity+-+when+you+can+hear+her+among+the+guest+stars&pqatl=google|title=All That Litters, 'Glitter'|last=Rodman|first=Sarah|work=Boston Herald|date=2001-09-11|accessdate=2011-02-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725010353/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/bostonherald/access/80313960.html?dids=80313960%3A80313960&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AFT&type=current&date=Sep+11%2C+2001&author=SARAH+RODMAN&pub=Boston+Herald&desc=Music%3B+All+that+litters+%60Glitter%27%3B+Carey+displays+newfound+maturity+-+when+you+can+hear+her+among+the+guest+stars&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-25}}</ref>，同时为《[[黑超特警組|黑超特警組]]》和《[[鬼靈精|鬼靈精]]》等作品写曲子<ref name="shapiro21"/>。《星梦泪痕》落入[[开发地狱|开发地狱]]后，凯莉推迟了计划，着手为新专辑准备素材<ref name="shapiro21"/>。[[索尼音樂娛樂|索尼音樂娛樂]]高管希望她准备假日季准备热门单曲精选集<ref name="shapiro22">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=115}}</ref>，希望发行一张囊括她在美国夺冠且在欧洲国际榜单打榜单曲的专辑，没有新曲，然而凯莉认为精选辑应该反映出她最个性化的歌曲，而不仅仅是她商业上最成功的歌曲。<ref name="shapiro23">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=116}}</ref>这张名为《[[獨一無二-白金冠軍單曲全選|獨一無二-白金冠軍單曲全選]]》（1998）囊括了她和[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮·休斯顿]]二重唱的电影《[[埃及王子|埃及王子]]》（1998）插曲《[[只要你相信|只要你相信]]》<ref name="shapiro23"/> 专辑在日本成为珍品，上架首周便售出100多万份，凯莉因此成为唯一一位达到这一功绩的国际艺人<ref name=japansales/>，仅过了头三个月，专辑在日本便售出325万份，创下非亚洲艺人的[[日本最暢銷專輯列表|最畅销专辑]]纪录<ref name=japansales>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yg0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA49|last=McClure|first=Steve|title=International News|work=Billboard|date=1999-01-23|accessdate=2010-10-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201173346/https://books.google.com/books?id=yg0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA49|archivedate=2018-02-01}}</ref>。

1999年春，凯莉着手创作她和索尼唱片签约的最后一张专辑<ref name="shapiro25">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=121}}</ref>。但压力所迫以及和索尼培养出的糟糕关系，她用1999年夏天的三个月完成了专辑，比她的其他专辑都要迅速<ref name="shapiro6"/>。 这张名叫《[[七色彩虹|七色彩虹]]》的专辑中，凯莉再度携手[[Jay_Z|Jay Z]]和{{tsl|en|DJ Clue?|DJ Clue?}}等一众音乐制作人和词曲作者<ref name="shapiro27">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=123}}</ref>。凯莉还抛开长期搭档亚方纳席耶夫，与[[大卫·沃尔特·福斯特|大卫·沃尔特·福斯特]]和{{tsl|en|Diane Warren|戴安娜·沃伦}}创作了两首民谣<ref name="shapiro27"/>。专辑于1999年11月2日发售，虽然在当时创下她职业生涯最高的首周销量纪录，但在《公告牌》二百强专辑榜上仅空降第二名<ref name="shapiro30">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=133}}</ref>。此时的凯莉和哥伦比亚唱片心存芥蒂，专辑头两首单曲过后，公司便叫停宣传<ref name="shapiro30"/>。他们认为《七色彩虹》并没有值得发行的强势单曲，然而凯莉希望发行一首民谣<ref name="shapiro30"/>。此举导致矛盾非常公开化，凯莉在她的网站贴出信息，向歌迷披露争端的内部信息，指引他们在电台点播《{{tsl|en|Can't Take That Away (Mariah's Theme)|Can't Take That Away|Can't Take That Away}}》<ref name="shapiro28">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=134}}</ref>。歌曲最终得以发行，不过凯莉发现歌曲只受到非常有限而且宣传少的发行，使得它在商业上无法存活<ref name="shapiro29">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=135}}</ref> 。专辑的评价普遍积极，《{{tsl|en|Sunday Herald|Sunday Herald}}》表示，专辑“表明她在灵魂民谣和与[[史努比狗狗|史努比狗狗]]和[[亚瑟小子|亚瑟小子]]等R&B重量级巨星的合作之间明显举棋不定......它是一张娴熟的流行灵魂乐合辑<ref>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/smgpubs/access/70150818.html?dids=70150818:70150818&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Nov+07%2C+1999&author=Graeme+Virtue&pub=Sunday+Herald&desc=Rainbow+Mariah+Carey+(Columbia)+HHH&pqatl=google|title=Rainbow: Mariah Carey (Columbia)|last=Graeme|first=Virtue|work=Sunday Herald|date=1999-11-07|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725044338/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/smgpubs/access/70150818.html?dids=70150818:70150818&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Nov+07%2C+1999&author=Graeme+Virtue&pub=Sunday+Herald&desc=Rainbow+Mariah+Carey+(Columbia)+HHH&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-25}}</ref>。”尽管商业上大获成功，专辑却创下她职业生涯最低专辑销量<ref name=fox>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,205054,00.html|title=Mariah Carey's Biography|last=Friedman|first=Roger|publisher=Fox News Channel|date=2008-04-03|accessdate=2011-08-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gk0lxlgy?url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,205054,00.html|archivedate=2013-05-19}}</ref>。

===2001–2004年：事業低潮- 《星夢淚痕》和《幸运手链》===
在获得[[公告牌音乐奖|公告牌十年艺人奖]]和世界音乐大奖千禧年最畅销女艺人奖后，<ref name="bestselling">{{cite web|url=http://www.montecarloresort.com/awards/00/w00res00.htm |title=Winners of the World Music Awards |publisher=Société des bains de mer de Monaco |accessdate=2010-08-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030621152238/http://www.montecarloresort.com/awards/00/w00res00.htm |archivedate=2003-06-21 }}</ref>凯莉离开了哥伦比亚，于2001年4月和[[维京唱片|美国维京唱片]]（[[EMI_Records|EMI Records]]）签订了1億美元的五年唱片录制合約<ref name=emi>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1777172.stm|title=EMI Drops Mariah Carey|publisher=BBC News|date=2002-01-31|accessdate=2011-02-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140513053826/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1777172.stm|archivedate=2014-05-13}}</ref>。凯莉也在此份合約中確保了自己可以掌握創作的概念和创意<ref name=emi />，避免重蹈覆轍。她选择录制一张結合了80年代迪斯科風格及其他相似風格的专辑，以配合电影的背景<ref>{{cite web|last=Erlewine|first=Stephen Thomas|url=http://allmusic.com/album/glitter-r544381|title=((( Glitter > Overview )))|publisher=AllMusic|accessdate=2011-02-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211235556/http://www.allmusic.com/album/glitter-r544381|archivedate=2011-02-11}}</ref>。她经常说哥伦比亚把她當商品來對待，她和摩托拉的分道扬镳恶化了她和公司高管的关系。几个月後，2001年7月，据广泛报道，凯莉身心交瘁，此外她还在个人网站上留下抱怨过度劳累的字眼<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,30577,00.html|title=Mariah Melts Down; Madonna Disappoints|last=Friedman|first=Roger|publisher=Fox News Channel|date=2001-07-26|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021075210/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,30577,00.html|archivedate=2012-10-21}}</ref>，同时结束了和歌手{{tsl|en|Luis Miguel|路易斯·米格尔}}长达三年的戀情<ref name="Luis Miguel Relationship">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/1335645/Let-me-sort-myself-out-singer-Carey-tells-fans.html|title=Let Me Sort Myself Out, Singer Carey Tells Fans|last=Davies|first=Hugh|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2001-07-28|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601174256/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/1335645/Let-me-sort-myself-out-singer-Carey-tells-fans.html|archivedate=2009-06-01}}</ref>。在次年的采访中，她表示：“我和那些不太了解我的人待在一起，没有私人助理，如果整天接受采访，晚上只能休息两个小时<ref name=stand>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/dcovfri.htm|title=Mariah Carey, 'Standing Again'|last=Gardner|first=Elysa|work=USA Today|date=2002-11-28|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111016211921/http://www.usatoday.com/life/dcovfri.htm|archivedate=2011-10-16}}</ref>。”媒体的压力、排满的工作安排表和与米格尔的分手，让凯莉在她的官方网站上发表一连串令人不安的消息，在几场现场宣传活动中出现古怪行为<ref name=nyc>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/01/24/us/record-label-pays-dearly-to-dismiss-mariah-carey.html|title=Record Label Pays Dearly To Dismiss Mariah Carey|last=Pareles|first=Jon|work=The New York Times|date=2002-01-22|accessdate=2011-02-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110128055201/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/01/24/us/record-label-pays-dearly-to-dismiss-mariah-carey.html|archivedate=2011-01-28}}</ref>。2001年7月19日 ，凯莉意外亮相[[音乐电视网|MTV]]节目《{{tsl|en|Total Request Live|互动全方位}}》<ref name=hospital>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1445424/mariah-carey-hospitalized.jhtml|title=Mariah Carey Hospitalized For 'Extreme Exhaustion'|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2011-03-29|date=2005-10-13|first=Jennifer|last=Vineyard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623213507/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1445424/mariah-carey-hospitalized.jhtml|archivedate=2012-06-23}}</ref>。播完广告后，节目主持[[卡森·达利|卡森·达利]]开始录影，此时凯莉穿着大号的男款衬衫，推着一个冰淇淋车登场，开始跳[[脫衣舞|脫衣舞]]，期间她脱掉衬衫，露出黄绿相间的紧身衣<ref name=hospital/>。后来她透露，她表演前，达利就知道她出现在大楼里。凯莉在节目中的亮相引起媒体强烈关注<ref name=nyc/>。仅过了几天，凯莉一反常态，开始在她的官方网站发布语音留言和消息：“现在我试着了解人生中的那些事儿，因此我不认为我应该立马做音乐。我只愿意休息一会儿，或是至少在没有人带着视频突然出现的前提下睡一个晚上。我真正想要的仅仅是做自己，这就是我应该放在第一位的事......这些话我不常说，但你猜怎么着，我没能照顾好自己<ref name=hospital/>。”之后消息被迅速删除，伯格评论称，发布这些文字时，凯莉“明显疲惫不堪，没有仔细思考”<ref name=hospital2>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1445918/mariah-carey-had-breakdown.jhtml|title=Mariah Carey Had 'Breakdown,' Her Publicist Says|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2011-03-29|date=2005-10-13|first=Jennifer|last=Vineyard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623213637/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1445918/mariah-carey-had-breakdown.jhtml|archivedate=2012-06-23}}</ref>。

[[File:Mariah_Carey_2003_tour_1.jpg|thumb]]》]]

7月26日，她突然住院，据称“极度疲惫”，“身心交瘁”<ref name=respect>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/77238866.html?dids=77238866:77238866&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug+09%2C+2001&author=Elysa+Gardner+and+Kelly+Carter&pub=USA+TODAY&desc=Mystery+shadows+Carey's+career+Pressures+linger+after+singer's+breakdown&pqatl=google|title=Mystery Shadows Carey's Career, Pressures Linger After Singer's Breakdown|last=Gardner|first=Elysa|work=USA Today|date=2001-09-09|accessdate=2011-06-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724232939/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/77238866.html?dids=77238866%3A77238866&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AFT&type=current&date=Aug+09%2C+2001&author=Elysa+Gardner+and+Kelly+Carter&pub=USA+TODAY&desc=Mystery+shadows+Carey%27s+career+Pressures+linger+after+singer%27s+breakdown&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-24}}</ref>。凯莉被送往康涅狄格州一家没有公开的医院，在医生的护理下住了两个星期，之后长期缺席公众视线。媒体极力报道凯莉宣传中断和住院后，维京唱片美国和[[二十世纪福斯|二十世纪福斯]]推迟了《[[星梦泪痕_(2001年电影)|星梦泪痕]]》及其同名原声带的发行<ref name=hospital2/><ref name=daily2>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/delay-dull-carey-glitter-article-1.931571|title=Delay May Dull Carey's 'Glitter'|last=Hutchinson|first=Bill|work=Daily News|date=2001-09-11|accessdate=2011-02-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122170157/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/delay-dull-carey-glitter-article-1.931571|archivedate=2015-11-22}}</ref>。谈及项目的商业反响不佳时，凯莉责备了她在发行期间的心境、项目的延期以及在[[九一一恐怖袭击|九一一恐怖袭击]]事件当天发行原声带<ref>{{cite web|title=Carey Blames 9/11 For 'Glitter' Flop|work=Digital Spy|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a199302/carey-blames-911-for-glitter-flop.html|last=Reynolds|first=Simon|date=2010-01-26|accessdate=2011-04-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100201061932/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a199302/carey-blames-911-for-glitter-flop.html|archivedate=2010-02-01}}</ref>。影片及其原声带遭到评论家的抨击，商业表现不佳<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/3671906/Mariah-Carey-Come-in-and-smell-the-perfume.html|title=Mariah Carey: Come in and Smell the Perfume|last=Patterson|first=Sylvia|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2000-03-17|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527053044/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/3671906/Mariah-Carey-Come-in-and-smell-the-perfume.html|archivedate=2010-05-27}}</ref>。原声带《{{tsl|en|Glitter (soundtrack)|星梦泪痕 (原声带)|星梦泪痕}}》当时成为凯莉销量最惨淡的专辑。《{{tsl|en|St. Louis Post-Dispatch|圣路易斯邮报}}》认为专辑不屑一提，“完全是垃圾，会演变成职业生涯一个恼人的污点，尽管没有一直饱受批评，但至少是几近成功的<ref>{{cite news|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SL&p_theme=sl&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EF07AA04681F07C&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=Mariah Carey's 'Glitter' is a Far Cry from Golden|last=Johnson|first=Kevin C.|work=St. Louis Post-Dispatch|date=2001-09-16|accessdate=2011-08-19|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225023637/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SL&p_theme=sl&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EF07AA04681F07C&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”之后的负面信息围绕着凯莉当时的私生活、该项目不遭人待见、和维京唱片（EMI Records）签订价值1亿美元的五张专辑的合约以5000万美元卖出<ref name=emi/><ref name=contract>{{cite news|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0F115C6D597A4809&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=Mariah Carries On With Record Deal, Recovery|last=Zwecker|first=Bill|work=Chicago Sun-Times|date=2002-01-22|accessdate=2011-06-16|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224050700/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0F115C6D597A4809&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不久后，凯莉飞到意大利[[卡普里岛|卡普里岛]]待五个月，按照过去一年来的个人经历，着手创作新专辑的素材<ref name=nyc/>。后来凯莉谈到她在维金的日子“完全是压力......看在钱的分上我仓促地做了一个决定，之前我是没有做过金钱方面的决定的。从那件事上我吸取了大教训<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/4690602.stm|title=The Fall and Rise of Mariah Carey|last=Adams|first=Josh|publisher=BBC News|date=2006-02-06|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511051402/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/4690602.stm|archivedate=2008-05-11}}</ref>。”当年晚些时候，她和[[小島唱片|小島唱片]]签了一份价值2400万多美元的合约<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/05/09/business/mariah-carey-and-universal-agree-to-terms-of-record-deal.html|title=Mariah Carey And Universal Agree to Terms Of Record Deal|last=Holson|first=Lisa|work=The New York Times|date=2002-02-21|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108155626/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/05/09/business/mariah-carey-and-universal-agree-to-terms-of-record-deal.html|archivedate=2012-11-08}}</ref>，启动唱片公司{{tsl|en|Monarc Entertainment||MonarC}}。从小很少联系过的父亲于当年[[癌症|癌症]]去世，进一步增添了凯莉的情感包袱<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.parade.com/articles/editions/2005/edition_06-05-2005/featured_0 |title=I Didn't Feel Worthy Of Happiness |last=Dotson |first=Rader |work=Parade |date=2005-05-05 |accessdate=2011-08-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101224100859/http://www.parade.com/articles/editions/2005/edition_06-05-2005/featured_0 |archivedate=2010-12-24 }}</ref>。

2002年，凯莉与[[米拉·索维诺|米拉·索维诺]]和{{tsl|en|Melora Walters||梅罗拉·沃特斯}}参演独立电影《{{tsl|en|WiseGirls|聪明女孩}}》，三人片中饰演了一家黑帮餐厅的侍应生。影片于[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]首映，口碑普遍较差，但凯莉饰演的角色获得褒扬。[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]的罗杰·弗莱德曼（{{lang|en|Roger Friedman}}）称凯莉是“新千禧年的{{tsl|en|Thelma Ritter|瑟尔玛·瑞特}}”，写道：“她的台词表达非常尖锐，能找到笑点<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,42928,00.html|last=Friedman|first=Roger|title=Mariah Makes Good in Mob Movie|publisher=Fox News Channel|date=2002-01-14|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314071924/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,42928,00.html|archivedate=2012-03-14}}</ref>。”随后，在路易斯安那州新奥尔良[[梅賽德斯-賓士超級巨蛋|路易斯安那超级巨蛋]]举办的[[第三十六届超级盃|第三十六届超级盃]]上演唱[[星条旗_(美国国歌)|美国国歌]]，获得热烈反响<ref name=europe>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/nypost/access/105343986.html?dids=105343986:105343986&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Feb+05%2C+2002&author=George+Willis&pub=New+York+Post&desc=SAFE+TO+SAY%2C+SUPER+BOWL+WAS+ONE+MAJOR+SUCCESS&pqatl=google|title=Safe To Say, Super Bowl Was One Major Success|last=Willis|first=George|work=New York Post|date=2002-02-05|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724215016/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/nypost/access/105343986.html?dids=105343986:105343986&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Feb+05%2C+2002&author=George+Willis&pub=New+York+Post&desc=SAFE+TO+SAY%2C+SUPER+BOWL+WAS+ONE+MAJOR+SUCCESS&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-24}}</ref>。2002年年末临近，凯莉发布了在她看来是“人生新契约”的全新录音室专辑《{{tsl|en|Charmbracelet||幸运手链}}》<ref name=stand/>。虽然选在《星梦泪痕》口碑反弹和凯莉回归音乐舞台的时候发行，专辑销量仍平平，凯莉的声线质量遭到批评。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》的琼·安德森称专辑“是她职业生涯最糟糕的作品，反映出的歌声，克服重力的嗓音和柔和的嘀咕声都不能承载<ref>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/403302181.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Sep+10%2C+2003&author=Joan+Anderman%2C+Globe+Staff&pub=Boston+Globe&desc=FOR+CAREY%2C+THE+GLORY'S+GONE+BUT+THE+GLITTER+LIVES+ON&pqatl=google|title=For Carey, the Glory's Gone but the Glitter Lives On|last=Anderman|first=Joan|work=Boston Globe|date=2003-09-10|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724215412/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/403302181.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AFT&type=current&date=Sep+10%2C+2003&author=Joan+Anderman%2C+Globe+Staff&pub=Boston+Globe&desc=FOR+CAREY%2C+THE+GLORY%27S+GONE+BUT+THE+GLITTER+LIVES+ON&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-24}}</ref>。”而[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]编辑{{tsl|en|Stephen Thomas Erlewine|斯蒂芬·托马斯·埃莱文}}的观点类似：“更大的问题是，凯莉的声音筋疲力尽，整张专辑听起来像是喋喋不休。她再也不能嘀咕或柔和地唱歌，或是演绎她那克服重力的标志性的嗓音<ref>{{cite web|last=Erlewine|first=Stephen Thomas|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/charmbracelet-r617273/review|title=((( Charmbracelet > Overview )))|publisher=AllMusic|date=2002-12-03|accessdate=2011-06-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gk0hvh2U?url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/charmbracelet-mw0000226447|archivedate=2013-05-19}}</ref>。”

2003年4月，凯莉宣布当年晚些时候巡演<ref name=vh1>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1472736/mariah-carey-maps-out-intimate-evening-tour/|title=Carey Maps Out 'Intimate Evening' Tour|last=Patel|first=Joseph|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2015-11-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127111201/http://www.mtv.com/news/1472736/mariah-carey-maps-out-intimate-evening-tour/|archivedate=2015-11-27}}</ref>。为期三个月的{{tsl|en|Charmbracelet World Tour|幸运手链世界巡演|幸运手链世界巡演：与玛丽亚·凯莉亲密接触之夜}}横跨北美和东亚，普遍在比竞技场稍小的场馆演出<ref name=vh2>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1471917/mariah-carey-scraps-arena-tour-opts-to-get-more-intimate/|title=Mariah Carey Scraps Arena Tour, Opts To Get More Intimate|last=Patel|first=Joseph|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2015-11-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127111204/http://www.mtv.com/news/1471917/mariah-carey-scraps-arena-tour-opts-to-get-more-intimate/|archivedate=2015-11-27}}</ref>。在北美期间，演出在剧院里完成，有点受百老汇的影响：“由于更加亲近，所以你会有一种和我共度良夜的经历<ref name=vh1/>。”然而，美国本土以外场次的表演制作规模小得多，凯利在亚洲和欧洲的体育场中，为3.5万名马尼拉、5万名马来西亚和7万多名中国观众表演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SJ&s_site=mercurynews&p_multi=SJ&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=1002404456D02378&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=Mariah's Malaysia Concert Ill-timed, Says Muslim Leader|work=San Jose Mercury News|date=2004-01-16|accessdate=2011-06-15|archive-date=2015-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150818174341/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SJ&s_site=mercurynews&p_multi=SJ&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=1002404456D02378&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凯莉也首次把英国站的巡演搬出伦敦，转向格拉斯哥、伯明翰和曼彻斯特<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2932336.stm|title=Mariah Adds UK To World Tour|publisher=BBC News|date=2003-05-31|accessdate=2011-02-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120802144702/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2932336.stm|archivedate=2012-08-02}}</ref>。巡演获得音评人和乐迷的赞扬，其中许多人称赞凯莉现场演绎的歌声以及制作整体质量<ref name=asilo>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=9LhjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=eyUMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1866,15841802&dq=mariah+carey+manila&hl=en|title=Mariah Carey Thrills Euphoric Manila Crowd|last=Asilo|first=Rito P.|work=Philippine Daily Inquirer|date=2003-11-23|accessdate=2011-06-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907214421/http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=9LhjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=eyUMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1866,15841802&dq=mariah+carey+manila&hl=en|archivedate=2013-09-07}}</ref>。

===2005–2007年：回歸與復仇- 《天后再臨-解放咪咪》===
