整个2004年，凯莉一直都在进行第10张录音室专辑《[[天后再臨-解放咪咪|天后再臨-解放咪咪]]》的创作。[[杰梅因·杜普里|杰梅因·杜普里]]、{{tsl|en|Bryan-Michael Cox|布赖恩-迈克尔·考克斯|布赖恩-迈克尔·考克斯}}、{{tsl|en|Manuel Seal|曼纽尔·席尔|曼纽尔·席尔}}、{{tsl|en|The Neptunes|海王星 (製作團隊)|海王星}}和[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]也加入了专辑的主要创作阵营。<ref name=viber/>《天后再臨-解放咪咪》發行後在多国夺冠，并获得了较好的乐评。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2005/apr/01/popandrock.shopping2|title=Mariah Carey, The Emancipation of Mimi|last=Sullivan|first=Caroline|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2005-04-01|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219102154/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2005/apr/01/popandrock.shopping2|archivedate=2013-12-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/reviews/2005-04-11-listen-up_x.htm|title=Mariah Rebounds, Garbage is Sweet, Will Smith Gets Lost|last=Gardner|first=Elysa|work=USA Today|date=2005-04-13|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524034213/http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/reviews/2005-04-11-listen-up_x.htm|archivedate=2011-05-24}}</ref>專輯的第二支單曲《[[我要我們在一起_(歌曲)|我要我們在一起]]》被認為是凱莉“職業生涯上被重新定義”<ref name=promo>{{cite web|url=http://business.highbeam.com/436102/article-1G1-141877770/jermaine-dupri-wins-rb-song-grammy-virgin-urban-music|title=Jermaine Dupri Wins R&B Song Grammy; Virgin Urban Music President Dupri Shares Songwriting Honors With Mariah Carey and So So Def/Virgin Artist Johnta Austin|publisher=[[Business_Wire|Business Wire]]. [[波克夏·哈薩威公司|Berkshire Hathaway]]|date=2006-04-16|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120611092331/http://business.highbeam.com/436102/article-1G1-141877770/jermaine-dupri-wins-rb-song-grammy-virgin-urban-music|archivedate=2012-06-11}}</ref>的一首歌曲。因為在當時，許多評論認為凱莉的生涯即將結束。<ref name=autogenerated5>{{cite web|last=Erlewine|first=Stephen Thomas|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/r729111|title=((( The Emancipation of Mimi > Overview )))|publisher=AllMusic|date=2005-04-12|accessdate=2011-08-19|archive-date=2013-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828175212/http://www.allmusic.com/album/r729111|dead-url=no}}</ref>樂評認為，這首歌曲使她“迴歸本原”<ref name=slanter>{{cite web|url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/mariah-carey-the-emancipation-of-mimi/560|title=Mariah Carey: The Emancipation Of Mimi|last=Cinquemani|first=Sal|work=Slant Magazine|date=2005-04-05|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111027201414/http://slantmagazine.com/music/review/mariah-carey-the-emancipation-of-mimi/560|archivedate=2011-10-27}}</ref>且“唱功回復”，<ref name=slanter/>而亦有評論認為，歌曲使凱莉作為[[谣曲|谣曲]]歌手的潛力復活。<ref name=viber>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FCcEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA139|title=Revolutions|last=Ehrlich|first=Dimitri|work=Vibe|date=2005-05-05|accessdate=2011-02-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101072137/https://books.google.com/books?id=FCcEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA139|archivedate=2016-01-01}}</ref>《我要我們在一起》在美國打破多項紀錄，是凱莉在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《公告牌》百强单曲榜]]奪冠的第16首單曲。<ref name=records>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sBMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA75|title=The Billboard Hot 100|last=Pietroluongo|first=Silvio|work=Billboard|date=2005-09-24|accessdate=2011-09-27|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101072137/https://books.google.com/books?id=sBMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA75|archivedate=2016-01-01}}</ref>歌曲在该榜单的冠軍位置停留了不連續的十四周，是{{tsl|en|List of Billboard Hot 100 chart achievements and milestones|公告牌百强单曲榜成就与里程碑列表|在该榜单夺冠周数第三长的歌曲}}。<ref name=records/>《告示牌》將其列為“十年之歌”，並將歌曲排在全時段最流行歌曲的第9名之位。<ref name=decade>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/decadeendcharts/2009/hot100-songs |title=The Billboard Hot 100 Singles & Tracks – Decade Year End Charts |work=Billboard |accessdate=2011-08-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110630055536/http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/decadeendcharts/2009/hot100-songs |archivedate=2011-06-30 }}</ref><ref name="yahoosales">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/specials/hot100/charts/top100-titles-10.shtml|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110925233024/http://www.billboard.com/specials/hot100/charts/top100-titles-10.shtml|archivedate=2011-09-25|title=The Billboard Hot 100 All-Time Top Songs (10-01)|work=Billboard|date=2010-09-24|accessdate=2011-09-27}}</ref>在榜單大獲成功的同時，歌曲亦打破了多項流媒體記錄。根據Nielsen BDS的數據，《我要我們在一起》是有史以來單日與單周收聽人次最多的歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/957598/ask-billboard-katy-perry-christina-aguilera-lady-gaga|last=Trust|first=Gary|title=Ask Billboard: Katy Perry, Christina Aguilera, Lady Gaga|work=Billboard|date=2010-06-25|accessdate=2011-08-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616001616/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/957598/ask-billboard-katy-perry-christina-aguilera-lady-gaga|archivedate=2013-06-16}}</ref>

在2005年9月25日期次的百强单曲榜中，《我要我們在一起》和凯莉的另一首单曲《{{tsl|en|Shake It Off (Mariah Carey song)|搖一搖}}》分居榜单前两位。至此，凯莉又创下了一项新纪录，成为首位个人演唱歌曲同时占据榜单冠亚军的女艺人。<ref name=records/>在2005年[[告示牌年終榜單|《告示牌》年終榜單]]中，凯莉第一次有歌曲在年终榜单获得了冠军。<ref name="US_yearend">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/yearendcharts/2005/hsititl.jsp |title=2005 Year End Charts – Hot 100 Songs |work=Billboard |date=2005-11-05 |accessdate=2011-07-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122230023/http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/yearendcharts/2005/hsititl.jsp |archivedate=2010-01-22 }}</ref>2006年至2007年，专辑获得了十项[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]提名。其中2006年是凯莉获得该奖提名最多的一年，这一年里凯莉共获得了八项提名。<ref name=usaawards>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/awards/grammys/2005-12-08-grammy-nominations_x.htm?loc=interstitialskip|title=Carey, West, Legend Lead The Grammy pack|last=Gundersen|first=Edna|work=USA Today|date=2005-12-08|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120114012858/http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/awards/grammys/2005-12-08-grammy-nominations_x.htm?loc=interstitialskip|archivedate=2012-01-14}}</ref>当年，凯莉以《天后再臨-解放咪咪》赢得了“{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best Contemporary R&B Album|格莱美奖最佳当代节奏蓝调专辑|最佳当代节奏蓝调专辑}}”，以《我要我們在一起》赢得了“{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best Female R&B Vocal Performance|格莱美奖最佳节奏蓝调女歌手|最佳节奏蓝调女歌手}}”和“{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best R&B Song|格莱美奖最佳节奏蓝调歌曲|最佳节奏蓝调歌曲}}”。<ref name=usaawards/>《天后再臨-解放咪咪》以接近500万份销量成为2005年美国最畅销的专辑，是自[[艾拉妮絲·莫莉塞特|艾拉妮絲·莫莉塞特]]1996年发布的专辑《{{tsl|en|Jagged Little Pill|小碎藥丸|小碎藥丸}}》以来由女性艺人发布的第一个年度最畅销专辑。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/article/2005/12/29/sorry_fiddy_mar/|title=Mariah Carey Has the Year's Top-selling CD|work=Entertainment Weekly|last=Susman|first=Gary|date=2005-12-29|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150918201318/http://www.ew.com/article/2005/12/29/sorry_fiddy_mar|archivedate=2015-09-18}}</ref>2005年年终，[[國際唱片業協會|國際唱片業協會]]报道称《天后再臨-解放咪咪》在全球已获得了超过770万份销量，是当年第二畅销的专辑，仅次于[[酷玩樂團|酷玩樂團]]的《[[X&Y|X&Y]]》。同时，专辑也是当年销量最高的个人专辑和由女性艺人发布的专辑。<ref name=world2005>{{cite web|url=http://www.musikindustrie.de/uploads/media/top50-2005.pdf|title=Top 50 Global Best Selling Albums for 2005|publisher=[[德國唱片業聯合會|Bundesverband Musikindustrie]]|accessdate=2017-02-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182610/http://www.musikindustrie.de/uploads/media/top50-2005.pdf|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4865716.stm|title=Coldplay Top 2005's Global Charts|publisher=BBC News|date=2006-03-31|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001023147/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4865716.stm|archivedate=2013-10-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/arts/story/2006/03/31/musicsales-coldplay.html |title=Coldplay Tops Worldwide Sales for 2005 |publisher=CBC News |date=2006-03-31 |accessdate=2011-08-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080617025339/http://www.cbc.ca/arts/story/2006/03/31/musicsales-coldplay.html |archivedate=2008-06-17 }}</ref>在[[第48届格莱美奖|第48届格莱美奖]]中，凯莉表演了《我要我們在一起》和《{{tsl|en|Fly Like a Bird|振翅高飛 (瑪麗亞·凱莉歌曲)|振翅高飛}}》的混合曲目。<ref name=nemn>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/access/983834771.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Feb+09%2C+2006&author=Ben+Rayner&pub=Toronto+Star&desc=Mariah+Carey%2C+meet+U2%2C+Kelly%3B+Comeback+stalled+as+U2+takes+five+Grammys+Canadians+come+up+empty-handed+at+awards+show&pqatl=google|title=Mariah Carey, Meet U2, Kelly; Comeback Stalled as U2 Takes five Grammys Canadians Come Up Empty-handed at Awards Show|last=Rayner|first=Ben|work=[[多倫多星報|Toronto Star]]|date=2005-12-09|accessdate=2011-05-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725044403/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/access/983834771.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Feb+09%2C+2006&author=Ben+Rayner&pub=Toronto+Star&desc=Mariah+Carey%2C+meet+U2%2C+Kelly%3B+Comeback+stalled+as+U2+takes+five+Grammys+Canadians+come+up+empty-handed+at+awards+show&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-25}}</ref>

为宣传专辑，凯莉开启了她第一场个人领衔巡演—{{tsl|en|The Adventures of Mimi|天后再臨世界巡迴演唱會}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://msnbc.msn.com/id/14190642/site/todayshow/ns/today-entertainment/t/mariah-carey-takes-madonna-new-tour/|title=Mariah Carey Takes on Madonna with New Tour|last=Popkin|first=Helen|publisher=MSNBC|date=2006-06-06|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110804214632/http://msnbc.msn.com/id/14190642/site/todayshow/ns/today-entertainment/t/mariah-carey-takes-madonna-new-tour/|archivedate=2011-08-04}}</ref>巡演在北美、非洲和亚洲多国共计巡回四十站，<ref name=mtvnews8>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1532213/mariah-carey-plots-mimis-touring-adventure.jhtml|title=Mariah Carey Plots Mimi's Touring Adventure|last=Vineyard|first=Jennifer|publisher=MTV News|date=2006-05-22|accessdate=2011-08-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623214117/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1532213/mariah-carey-plots-mimis-touring-adventure.jhtml|archivedate=2012-06-23}}</ref>获得了乐评界与音乐会界较好的评价。他们称赞了凯莉现场表演品质的提升以及巡演整场的设计。<ref name=outshines>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1537972/mariah-carey-tour-kickoff-all-about-voice.jhtml|title=Mariah Carey Tour Kickoff: The Voice Outshines Costume Changes, Video Clips|last=Vineyard|first=Jennifer|publisher=MTV News|date=2006-08-30|accessdate=2011-08-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623213753/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1537972/mariah-carey-tour-kickoff-all-about-voice.jhtml|archivedate=2012-06-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/access/1105356491.html?dids=1105356491:1105356491&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug+24%2C+2006&author=RAFER+GUZMN.+STAFF+WRITER&pub=Newsday+(Combined+editions)&desc=Mimi+hits+the+Garden%2C+just+like+that&pqatl=google|title=Mimi Hits the Garden, Just Like That|last=Rafer|first=Guzman|work=Newsday|date=2006-09-10|accessdate=2011-08-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725034317/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/access/1105356491.html?dids=1105356491:1105356491&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug+24%2C+2006&author=RAFER+GUZMN.+STAFF+WRITER&pub=Newsday+(Combined+editions)&desc=Mimi+hits+the+Garden%2C+just+like+that&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-25}}</ref>其中，凯莉在[[突尼斯市|突尼斯市]]的表演中吸引了大约60,000名粉丝观看。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mariahcarey.com/news/15321|title='Comeback' Succeeded For Carey In Tunis|publisher=Mariahcarey.com|date=2006-07-27|accessdate=2011-08-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111003150127/http://mariahcarey.com/news/15321|archivedate=2011-10-03 }}</ref>2007年，巡演的[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]《{{tsl|en|The Adventures of Mimi (video)|天后再臨世界巡迴演唱會 (影片)|天后再臨世界巡迴演唱會}}》发行。

=== 2008–2009年：延續熱度- 《蝴蝶效應》、《不完美天使》和《珍藏》===
2007年春，凯莉在她个人的[[安圭拉|安圭拉]]别墅开始着手准备自己的第11张录音室专辑《[[蝴蝶效應_(專輯)|蝴蝶效應]]》。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/pagesix/cindy_adams/item_QYji9hBaJmhBk7ito9jshO;jsessionid=3036AFA318523D15C26D85EFEFAC2961 |title=Yes On Dubya Apology Frost |last=Starr |first=Michael |work=[[紐約郵報|New York Post]] |date=2008-04-19 |accessdate=2011-05-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111222300/http://www.nypost.com/p/pagesix/cindy_adams/item_QYji9hBaJmhBk7ito9jshO;jsessionid=3036AFA318523D15C26D85EFEFAC2961 |archivedate=2012-01-11 }}</ref>虽然专辑发行后收获了众多乐评的好评，<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2008/apr/11/popandrock.alexispetridis|title=Mariah Carey: E=MC²|last=Macpherson|first=Alex|work=The Guardian|date=2008-04-16|accessdate=2011-08-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219104201/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2008/apr/11/popandrock.alexispetridis|archivedate=2013-12-19}}</ref>但有些乐评批评了专辑与《天后再臨-解放咪咪》过于相似。<ref name=angels>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/music/la-et-mariah12apr12,1,6445816.story|title=CD: Mariah Carey's 'E=MC2'|last=Richard|first=David|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2008-04-08|accessdate=2011-08-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522151202/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/music/la-et-mariah12apr12,1,6445816.story|archivedate=2011-05-22}}</ref>在专辑发行前两周，《[[零距离接触|零距离接触]]》作为专辑的第一张单曲发行。歌曲在百强单曲榜夺冠，是凯莉在该榜单第18首冠军单曲，使凯莉成为在该榜单{{tsl|en|List of artists by number of Billboard Hot 100 number one singles|各艺人在公告牌百强单曲榜取得的冠军单曲数列表|取得最多冠军单曲的女性歌手}}。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/23918924/ns/today-entertainment/t/mariah-carey-surpasses-elvis-no-s/|title=Elvis is Spotted – Rolling in His Grave|last=Guthrie|first=Marisa|work=Daily News|date=2008-04-04|accessdate=2011-08-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003081203/http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/23918924/ns/today-entertainment/t/mariah-carey-surpasses-elvis-no-s/|archivedate=2