ps://web.archive.org/web/20170107173020/http://ew.com/article/2013/11/13/mariah-carey-american-idol-hated/|archivedate=2017-01-07}}</ref>影視方面，凱莉出演了2013年電影《[[白宫管家|白宫管家]]》，<ref>{{cite web |last=Buchanan |first=Kyle |url=http://www.vulture.com/2012/07/mariah-carey-is-joining-the-butler.html |title=Mariah Carey Is Joining The Butler |publisher=Vulture |date=2012-07-26 |accessdate=2012-08-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120828123954/http://www.vulture.com/2012/07/mariah-carey-is-joining-the-butler.html |archivedate=2012-08-28 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Brooks |first=Brian |url=https://movies.yahoo.com/news/mariah-carey-joins-butler-lionsgate-aims-time-again-203039567.html |title=Mariah Carey Joins The Butler; Lionsgate Aims for Time and Again: Biz Break |publisher=Yahoo! |date=2012-07-26 |accessdate=2013-06-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017110722/http://movies.yahoo.com/news/mariah-carey-joins-butler-lionsgate-aims-time-again-203039567.html |archivedate=2013-10-17 }}</ref>還獻聲[[客串|客串]]了成人動畫系列《[[特工老爹|特工老爹]]》中的一名[[大老粗|大老粗]]。<ref>{{cite web |last=Francis |first=Nathan |url=http://www.inquisitr.com/1024011/mariah-carey-to-become-a-cartoon-character-on-american-dad/ |title=Mariah Carey To Become A Cartoon Character On 'American Dad' |publisher=Inquisitr |accessdate=2013-11-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109161859/http://www.inquisitr.com/1024011/mariah-carey-to-become-a-cartoon-character-on-american-dad/ |archivedate=2013-11-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurweb.com/2013/08/mariah-carey-to-voice-redneck-on-american-dad/ |title=Mariah Carey to Voice Redneck on 'American Dad' |publisher=EURweb |date=2013-08-02 |accessdate=2013-08-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130804060509/http://www.eurweb.com/2013/08/mariah-carey-to-voice-redneck-on-american-dad/ |archivedate=2013-08-04 }}</ref>

