2015年1月15日，凱莉宣佈將在{{tsl|en|The Colosseum at Caesars Palace|拉斯維加斯凱撒宮}}舉辦駐唱表演{{tsl|en|Number 1 to Infinity (residency show)|真愛永恆 (駐唱演出)|真愛永恆}}。<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6436789/mariah-carey-announces-caesars-palace-residency|title=Mariah Carey Announces Caesars Palace Residency|work=Billboard|date=2015-01-15|accessdate=2015-04-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408072810/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6436789/mariah-carey-announces-caesars-palace-residency|archivedate=2015-04-08}}</ref>1月30日，凱莉宣佈離開[[环球唱片|環球音樂]]的[[Def_Jam唱片|Def Jam唱片]]，並重新與[[索尼音樂|索尼音樂]]的[[史诗唱片|史诗唱片]]簽約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2015/01/30/mariah-carey-reunites-with-la-reid-at-epic-records/|title=Mariah Carey reunites with L.A. Reid at Epic Records|date=2015-01-30|work=Rap-Up|accessdate=2015-01-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131221035/http://www.rap-up.com/2015/01/30/mariah-carey-reunites-with-la-reid-at-epic-records/|archivedate=2015-01-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/6457962/mariah-carey-epic-records-deal-la-reid-sony-music|title=The Inside Story of How Mariah Carey and L.A. Reid Reunited (at a Fraction of Her Former $80 Million Deal)|date=2015-01-30|accessdate=2015-01-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202021535/http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/6457962/mariah-carey-epic-records-deal-la-reid-sony-music|archivedate=2015-02-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Mariah Carey announces Las Vegas residency|url=http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2015/01/15/mariah-carey-announces-las-vegas-residency/|accessdate=2015-02-01|publisher=Fox News Channel|agency=[[福斯娱乐集团|Fox Entertainment Group]] ([[二十一世紀福斯|21st Century Fox]])|date=2015-01-25|location=United States|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150116092047/http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2015/01/15/mariah-carey-announces-las-vegas-residency/|archivedate=2015-01-16}}</ref>

為宣傳駐唱，凱莉發行了同名[[精選輯|精選輯]]《[[真愛永恆_冠軍精選+新歌|真愛永恆]]》，專輯收錄了凱莉18首[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百强单曲榜]]冠軍單曲，並額外收錄了一首新歌曲《{{tsl|en|Infinity (Mariah Carey song)|真愛永恆 (歌曲)|真愛永恆}}》，這首歌曲於4月27日作為單曲發行。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hampp|first1=Andrew|title=Mariah Carey Announces Release Date, Tracklist For '#1 To Infinity'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/6531609/mariah-carey-release-date-tracklist-1-to-infinity|accessdate=2015-04-23|work=Billboard|date=2015-04-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417001629/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/6531609/mariah-carey-release-date-tracklist-1-to-infinity|archivedate=2015-04-17}}</ref>2015年12月，凱莉在聖誕電影《{{tsl|en|A Christmas Melody|聖誕天籟|聖誕天籟}}》中扮演梅丽莎一角。<ref>{{cite web|title = Mariah Carey as a Shady PTA Mom in Hallmark's A Christmas Melody Is Peak Mariah Carey|url = http://www.vh1.com/news/232238/mariah-carey-hallmark-movie/|publisher = [[VH1|VH1]]|accessdate = 2015-12-20|date = 2015-12-19|first = Christopher|last = Rosa|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222121446/http://www.vh1.com/news/232238/mariah-carey-hallmark-movie/|archivedate = 2015-12-22}}</ref>同月，凱莉宣佈，新一輪巡演{{tsl|en|The Sweet Sweet Fantasy Tour|甜蜜蜜夢幻巡迴演唱會}}將在2016年3月開啟。巡演包括25場演出，是凱莉在13年來在歐洲開的第一場巡演。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6806105/mariah-carey-sweet-sweet-fantasy-2016-tour-dates|title=Mariah Carey Announces Sweet Sweet Fantasy 2016 European Tour|date=2015-12-14|first=Luis|last=Polanco|work=Billboard|accessdate=2017-01-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170128020810/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6806105/mariah-carey-sweet-sweet-fantasy-2016-tour-dates|archivedate=2017-01-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.refinery29.uk/2016/03/106757/mariah-carey-sweet-sweet-fantasy-tour-review-news|title=What Goes Down On Mariah's Sweet Sweet Fantasy Tour|first=Olivia|last=Marks|date=2016-03-24|publisher={{tsl|en|Refinery29||Refinery29}}|accessdate=2017-01-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108093400/http://www.refinery29.uk/2016/03/106757/mariah-carey-sweet-sweet-fantasy-tour-review-news|archivedate=2017-01-08}}</ref>

2016年3月15日，凱莉表示自己正在拍攝一部名為《{{tsl|en|Mariah's World|瑪麗亞的世界}}》的記錄電影。電影記錄了甜蜜蜜夢幻巡迴演唱會中歐洲演出的細節和凱莉的結婚計畫。凱莉告訴《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》：“我覺得這會是展示我個性和自我的好機會，即便我感覺我真正的粉絲已經知道我是什麼樣的人了……但仍然有許多人對這些有誤解。”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Koblin|first1=John|title=Mariah Carey to star in a series for E!|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/16/arts/television/mariah-carey-to-star-in-a-series-for-e.html?smid=tw-nytimes&smtyp=cur&_r=0|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2017-01-07|date=2016-03-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801130740/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/16/arts/television/mariah-carey-to-star-in-a-series-for-e.html?smid=tw-nytimes&smtyp=cur&_r=0|archivedate=2017-08-01}}</ref>影片於2016年12月4日正式首播。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-et-st-mariahs-world-mariah-carey-e-20160803-snap-htmlstory.html |title=It's 'Mariah's World' and everyone else is just living in it |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2016-08-03 |first=Libby |last=Hill |accessdate=2016-09-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917203122/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-et-st-mariahs-world-mariah-carey-e-20160803-snap-htmlstory.html |archivedate=2016-09-17 }}</ref>2016年10月5日，凱莉友情客串音樂戲劇《[[嘻哈帝国|嘻哈帝国]]》中一名超級巨星歌手吉蒂，並與{{tsl|en|Jussie Smollett|朱西·斯莫利特|朱西·斯莫利特}}合作演唱了歌曲《Infamous》。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bentley|first1=Jean|title=Empire Needed Much More Mariah Carey|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/800128/empire-needed-much-more-mariah-carey|work={{tsl|en|E! Online||E! Online}}|accessdate=2016-10-06|date=2016-10-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006090148/http://www.eonline.com/news/800128/empire-needed-much-more-mariah-carey|archivedate=2016-10-06}}</ref>2016年12月5日，凱莉與[[凡妮莎·威廉斯|凡妮莎·威廉斯]]、[[夏卡·康|夏卡·康]]、[[佩蒂·拉貝爾|佩蒂·拉貝爾]]和{{tsl|en|Teyana Taylor|泰雅娜·泰勒|泰雅娜·泰勒}}在{{tsl|en|VH1 Divas|VH1天后|VH1天后}}慈善演唱會《假日：不安靜之夜》表演。<ref name="vh1.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.vh1.com/news/289260/mariah-carey-vh1-divas-holiday/|title=Mariah Carey to Perform at VH1 Divas Holiday: Unsilent Night|publisher=VH1|first=Jasmine|date=2016-11-03|last=Washington|accessdate=2016-12-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206020331/http://www.vh1.com/news/289260/mariah-carey-vh1-divas-holiday/|archivedate=2016-12-06}}</ref>

2016年12月31日，凱莉在《[[迪克·克拉克的跨年搖滾夜|迪克·克拉克的跨年搖滾夜]]》進行表演。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》將這場表演形容為“表演車禍”。<ref>{{cite web|title=Mariah Carey’s New Year's Eve Nightmare in Times Square|first=Patrick|last=Healy|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/01/arts/music/mariah-carey-new-years-eve-times-square.html|work=The New York Times|date=2017-01-01|accessdate=2017-01-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101113504/http://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/01/arts/music/mariah-carey-new-years-eve-times-square.html|archivedate=2017-01-01}}</ref>表演過程中，凱莉的[[入耳式耳機|入耳式耳機]]發生故障。由於故障，凱莉無法聽見音樂聲，在人聲仍在播放的時候停止了演唱，造成[[假唱|假唱]]被發現。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/music/mariah-carey-shakes-off-new-year-s-eve-debacle-in-times-square-1.12835880|title=Mariah Carey shakes off New Year’s Eve debacle in Times Square|date=2017-01-01|accessdate=2017-01-02|work={{tsl|en|Newsday||Newsday}}|first=Glenn|last=Gamboa|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101174746/http://www.newsday.com/entertainment/music/mariah-carey-shakes-off-new-year-s-eve-debacle-in-times-square-1.12835880|archivedate=2017-01-01}}</ref>但凱莉團隊和{{tsl|en|Dick Clark Productions|迪克·克拉克製作公司}}均對事件的指責表示否認。<ref>{{cite web|title=Mariah Carey's Rep Says 'Rockin' Eve' Producers 'Set Her Up to Fail'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7640608/mariah-carey-rep-technical-problems-bungle-new-years-show-dick-clark|work=Billboard|date=2017-01-01|accessdate=2017-01-01|first=Michele Amabile|last=Angermiller|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102013500/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7640608/mariah-carey-rep-technical-problems-bungle-new-years-show-dick-clark|archivedate=2017-01-02}}</ref>

2017年2月3日，凯莉发行{{le|YG (说唱歌手)|YG (rapper)|YG}}客串的歌曲《{{le|我不乐意|I Don't (Mariah Carey song)}}》<ref>{{cite web|last=Platton|first=Adelle|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/7676270/mariah-carey-yg-i-dont-cover-art|title=Mariah Carey Reveals Cover Art for YG-Assisted 'I Don't'|work=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|date=2017-01-31|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6o3YIgl5l?url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/7676270/mariah-carey-yg-i-dont-cover-art|archivedate=2017-02-05}}</ref>。那个月晚些时候，为动画电影《[[乐高蝙蝠侠大电影|乐高蝙蝠侠大电影]]》献声哥谭市市长一角<ref>{{cite news|last1=Galuppo|first1=Mia|title=Mariah Carey Joins 'The Lego Batman Movie'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/mariah-carey-joins-lego-batman-838356|accessdate=2015-11-10|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2015-11-09|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108173521/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/mariah-carey-joins-lego-batman-838356|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年4月，凯莉新厂牌花蝴蝶MC唱片成立，史诗唱片加盟合作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2017/04/10/mariah-carey-announces-a-new-album-and-forms-her-own-record-label/|title=Mariah Carey Announces A New Album And Forms Her Own Record Label|first=Hugh|last=McIntyre|work=Forbes|date=2017-04-10|accessdate=2017-08-13|archive-date=2018-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180215025201/https://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2017/04/10/mariah-carey-announces-a-new-album-and-forms-her-own-record-label/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年7月，凯莉客串[[奎恩·拉提法|奎恩·拉提法]]、[[潔達·蘋姬·史密斯|潔達·蘋姬·史密斯]]和{{le|瑞吉纳·霍尔|Regina Hall}}出演的喜剧片《{{le|闺蜜假期|Girls Trip}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/movies/2017/07/12/girls-trip-ew-review/|title=''Girls Trip'' is raucous, raunchy fun: EW review|first=Devan|last=Coggan|date=2017-07-12|accessdate=2017-08-13|work=Entertainment Weekly|archive-date=2017-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170713002701/http://ew.com/movies/2017/07/12/girls-trip-ew-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同一个月，凯莉和[[莱昂纳尔·里奇|莱昂纳尔·里奇]]启动{{le|大热金曲巡演|All the Hits Tour (Lionel Richie and Mariah Carey)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/7718051/lionel-richie-mariah-carey-rescheduled-concert-dates|title=Lionel Richie & Mariah Carey Announce Rescheduled Tour Dates|first=Dave|last=Brooks|date=2017-03-09|work=Billboard|accessdate=2017-08-13|archive-date=2017-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170310040045/http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/7718051/lionel-richie-mariah-carey-rescheduled-concert-dates|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凯莉还和[[斯韦·李|斯韦·李]]一道客串[[弗伦奇·蒙塔纳|弗伦奇·蒙塔纳]]单曲《Unforgettable》<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lamarre|first1=Carl|title=Mariah Carey Adds Her Sweet Touch to French Montana's Acoustic 'Unforgettable (Remix)': Listen|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/7942002/french-montana-unforgettable-remix-mariah-carey|website=Billboard|accessdate=2017-10-23|archive-date=2017-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829004935/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/7942002/french-montana-unforgettable-remix-mariah-carey|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年10月，凯莉发布电影《[[圣诞星|圣诞星]]》同名歌曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7881128/mariah-carey-the-star-movie-trailer-new-song|title=Mariah Carey Offers Up a Taste of New Christmas Song in 'The Star' Teaser Trailer|work=Billboard|first=Liza|last=Shcherbakova|date=2017-07-26|accessdate=2017-08-12|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730094403/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7881128/mariah-carey-the-star-movie-trailer-new-song|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凯莉还开发了圣诞动画电影《圣诞节我只要你》（{{lang|en|''Mariah Carey's All I Want For Christmas Is You''}}），并录制电影歌曲《小雪人》（{{lang|en|"Lil' Snowman"}}）。电影于2017年11月14日[[录影带首映|录影带首映]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/mariah-careys-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-to-become-film-w473081|title=Mariah Carey's 'All I Want for Christmas Is You' to Become Animated Film|first=Brittany|last=Spanos|date=2017-03-21|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2017-08-12|archive-date=2017-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129102541/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/mariah-careys-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-to-become-film-w473081|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Holub|first1=Christian|title=Watch the first trailer for Mariah Carey's All I Want For Christmas Is You movie|url=http://ew.com/music/2017/09/06/mariah-carey-christmas-movie-trailer/|website=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2017-10-23|archive-date=2017-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023230143/http://ew.com/music/2017/09/06/mariah-carey-christmas-movie-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，她继续{{le|圣诞节我只要你：欢乐和喜庆之夜|
All I Want for Christmas Is You: A Night of Joy and Festivity}}巡回演唱会，首次在英国和法国等国开场<ref>{{cite web|last1=Giannotta|first1=Meghan|title=Mariah Carey sets dates for Christmas tour at Beacon Theatre|url=https://www.amny.com/entertainment/mariah-carey-sets-dates-for-christmas-tour-at-beacon-theatre-1.14347656|website=AM New York|accessdate=2017-10-23|archive-date=2017-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004210714/https://www.amny.com/entertainment/mariah-carey-sets-dates-for-christmas-tour-at-beacon-theatre-1.14347656|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2017年12月31日，歌手回归《迪克·克拉克的跨年搖滾夜》，《纽约时报》认为这是“电视制作流行文化救赎行为”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Deb|first1=Sopan|title=Mariah Carey Redeems Herself on New Year's Eve in Times Square|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/01/arts/mariah-carey-new-years-eve.html|accessdate=2018-09-17|work=The New York Times|date=2018-01-01|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226191414/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/01/arts/mariah-carey-new-years-eve.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2018-至今：《流行警报》、《祝福》25周年、入選“作曲家名人堂”、出道30週年紀念===
2018年，凯莉和[[Live_Nation_Entertainment|Live Nation Entertainment]]签署全球协议<ref>{{cite web|title=Mariah Carey Signs Major Deal With Live Nation Entertainment|url=http://thatgrapejuice.net/2018/05/mariah-carey-signs-major-deal-with-live-nation-entertainment/|website=ThatGrapeJuice|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2018-05-10|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224163230/https://thatgrapejuice.net/2018/05/mariah-carey-signs-major-deal-with-live-nation-entertainment/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。协议的第一项承诺是在拉斯维加斯召开新的驻场演唱会。这个名为“{{le|花蝴蝶归来|The Butterfly Returns}}”的演出于2018年7月登场，获得广泛好评<ref>{{cite web|last1=Carr|first1=Mary Kate|title=Mariah Carey announces new Las Vegas residency 'The Butterfly Returns'|url=https://ew.com/music/2018/04/30/mariah-carey-las-vegas-residency-the-butterfly-returns/|website=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2018-04-30|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306183138/https://ew.com/music/2018/04/30/mariah-carey-las-vegas-residency-the-butterfly-returns/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Sheckells|first1=Melinda|title=Mariah Carey Kicks Off Her 'The Butterfly Returns' Vegas Residency With Strong Opening Weekend|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8464350/mariah-carey-las-vegas-residency-the-butterfly-returns-review|website=Billboard|accessdate=2018-09-17|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308212554/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8464350/mariah-carey-las-vegas-residency-the-butterfly-returns-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。迄今为止的17场演出票房收入360万美元<ref>{{cite web |title=Top 10 Highest Grossing Las Vegas Residencies Of All Time: Celine Dion, Britney Spears, Elton John and More |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8491648/highest-grossing-las-vegas-residencies |website=Billboard |accessdate=2018-12-28 |date=2018-12-27 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205194734/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8491648/highest-grossing-las-vegas-residencies |dead-url=no }}</ref>。演唱会后，凯莉启动“{{le|玛丽亚·凯莉：演唱会现场|Mariah Carey: Live in Concert}}”亚洲巡演，“圣诞节我只要你”欧洲系列巡演也会回归<ref>{{cite web|title=Mariah Carey adds Kuala Lumpur and Singapore to 2018 Asia tour|url=https://asialive365.com/mariah-carey-kl-singapore-2018/|website=Asia Live 365|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2018-04-20|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710053009/https://asialive365.com/mariah-carey-kl-singapore-2018/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Ellwood-Hughes|first1=Pip|title=Mariah Carey is bringing her All I Want for Christmas Is You Tour back to Europe this December|url=https://www.entertainment-focus.com/music-section/music-news/mariah-carey-is-bringing-her-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-tour-back-to-europe-this-december/|website=Entertainment Focus|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2018-06-04|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710051242/https://www.entertainment-focus.com/music-section/music-news/mariah-carey-is-bringing-her-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-tour-back-to-europe-this-december/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巡演期间，索尼音乐亚太区代表向凯莉颁发亚太区16亿销量证书<ref>{{cite web |title=Mariah Carey Honored for 1.6 Billion Asia Sales, Adds World Tour Dates |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/international/8481619/mariah-carey-asia-world-tour-dates |publisher=Billboard |accessdate=2019-01-01 |date=2018-10-24 |archive-date=2021-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306070501/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/international/8481619/mariah-carey-asia-world-tour-dates |dead-url=no }}</ref>。“圣诞节我只要你”的现场画面在[[YouTube|YouTube]]发布<ref>{{cite web |last1=Darmon |first1=Aynslee |title=Mariah Carey Releases Live Performance Of ‘All I Want For Christmas Is You’ From European Tour |publisher=Entertainment Tonight Canada |url=https://etcanada.com/news/399982/mariah-carey-releases-live-performance-of-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-from-european-tour/ |accessdate=2019-01-01 |date=2018-12-21 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920102358/https://etcanada.com/news/399982/mariah-carey-releases-live-performance-of-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-from-european-tour/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年9月，凯莉宣布计划同年发行个人第十五张录音室专辑.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Gillespie|first1=Katherine|title=Mariah Carey Is Releasing New Music|url=http://www.papermag.com/mariah-carey-new-song-gtfo-2604261274.html|website=Paper|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2018-09-12|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307192758/https://www.papermag.com/mariah-carey-new-song-gtfo-2604261274.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|title=LEGENDARY GLOBAL ICON MARIAH CAREY RETURNS WITH NEW MUSIC|url=https://www.epicrecords.com/legendary-global-icon-mariah-carey-returns-with-new-music/|website=Epic Records|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2018-09-13|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308150813/https://www.epicrecords.com/legendary-global-icon-mariah-carey-returns-with-new-music/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新单曲《{{le|從我眼前消失|GTFO (song)}}》在项目公布时发布<ref>{{cite web|last1=Yoo|first1=Noah|last2=Monroe|first2=Jazz|title=Mariah Carey Returns With New Song From Album Out This Year: Listen|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/mariah-carey-returns-with-new-song-from-album-out-this-year-listen/|website=Pitchfork|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2018-09-13|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308081023/https://pitchfork.com/news/mariah-carey-returns-with-new-song-from-album-out-this-year-listen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该曲于2018年9月21日{{le|iHeartRadio音乐节|iHeartRadio Music Festival}}上首演<ref>{{cite web|last1=Aniftos|first1=Rania|title=Justin Timberlake, Mariah Carey, Jack White & Carrie Underwood Lead iHeartRadio Music Festival 2018 Lineup|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/festivals/8459350/iheartradio-music-festival-2018-lineup-justin-timberlake-mariah-carey|website=Billboard|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2018-06-05|archive-date=2018-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921002634/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/festivals/8459350/iheartradio-music-festival-2018-lineup-justin-timberlake-mariah-carey|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主打歌《{{le|與你廝守|With You (Mariah Carey song)}}》10月发行，于{{le|2018年全美音乐奖|American Music Awards of 2018}}首演<ref>{{cite web |title=Mariah Carey Performs New Single 'With You' for the First on TV at 2018 AMAs |url=https://www.billboard.com/video/mariah-carey-performs-new-single-with-you-for-the-first-on-tv-at-2018-amas-billboard-news |website=Billboard |accessdate=2018-10-16 |date=2018-10-09 |archive-date=2019-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611013418/https://www.billboard.com/video/mariah-carey-performs-new-single-with-you-for-the-first-on-tv-at-2018-amas-billboard-news |dead-url=no }}</ref>。单曲是九年来凯莉在美国[[当代成人单曲榜|当代成人单曲榜]]上非假日成绩最好的作品<ref>{{cite web |title=Mariah Carey Chart History - Adult Contemporary |url=https://www.billboard.com/music/Mariah-Carey/chart-history/adult-contemporary/3 |publisher=Billboard |accessdate=2019-01-01 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309034216/https://www.billboard.com/music/Mariah-Carey/chart-history/adult-contemporary/3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是十年来在{{le|成人节奏布鲁斯单曲榜|Adult R&B Songs}}上成绩最好的歌曲<ref>{{cite web |title=Mariah Carey Chart History - Adult R&B Songs |url=https://www.billboard.com/music/mariah-carey/chart-history/hot-adult-r-and-b-airplay |publisher=Bilboard |accessdate=2019-01-02 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308225147/https://www.billboard.com/music/mariah-carey/chart-history/hot-adult-r-and-b-airplay |dead-url=no }}</ref>。后来在10月，凯莉宣布新专辑名字<ref name="Caution">{{cite news|last=Pedrosa|first=Marina|title=Mariah Carey Announces New Album ''Caution''|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8479876/mariah-carey-announces-caution-album-release-date|accessdate=2018-10-15|work=Billboard|date=2018-10-15|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126134552/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8479876/mariah-carey-announces-caution-album-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>，发行说唱歌手{{le|Ty Dolla Sign|Ty Dolla Sign}}客串的宣传单曲《The Distance》。在这之前，单曲《{{le|萬萬不可|A No No}}》发布<ref>{{cite web |last1=Blistein |first1=Jon |title=Hear Mariah Carey Tap Ty Dolla $ign, Skrillex for New Song ‘The Distance’ |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/mariah-carey-ty-dolla-sign-skrillex-new-song-the-distance-744257/ |publisher=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2019-01-01 |date=2018-10-18 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127124046/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/mariah-carey-ty-dolla-sign-skrillex-new-song-the-distance-744257/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Blistein |first1=Jon |title=Hear Mariah Carey Reinvent Lil Kim Classic on New Song ‘A No No’ |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/mariah-carey-new-song-a-no-no-750445/ |publisher=Rolling Stone |accessdate=2019-01-01 |date=2018-11-01 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117231712/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/mariah-carey-new-song-a-no-no-750445/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。专辑名为《{{le|流行警报|Caution (Mariah Carey album)}}》，2018年11月16日发行，获得海内外评论人好评<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/music/caution/mariah-carey |title=Caution by Mariah Carey Critic Reviews and Tracks |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2019-01-01 |archive-date=2018-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117104856/https://www.metacritic.com/music/caution/mariah-carey |dead-url=no }}</ref>。专辑是凯莉对之前作品风格的微调<ref>{{cite web |last1=Johnston |first1=Maura |title=Mariah Carey: Caution Album Review |url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/mariah-carey-caution/ |website=Pitchfork |accessdate=2019-01-01 |date=2018-11-22 |archive-date=2018-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181210081147/https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/mariah-carey-caution/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有新鲜感，“挑衅得令人愉快”<ref>{{cite web |last1=Greenblatt |first1=Leah |title=Mariah Carey is pleasingly defiant on Caution |url=https://ew.com/music/2018/11/16/mariah-carey-caution-review/ |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2019-01-01 |date=2018-11-16 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608003744/https://ew.com/music/2018/11/16/mariah-carey-caution-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年12月，专辑入选多家音乐媒体和评论人的年终榜单<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/feature/critics-pick-top-10-best-albums-of-2018|title=Best of 2018: Music Critic Top Ten Lists|website=Metacritic|accessdate=2019-01-01|archive-date=2019-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190118141439/https://www.metacritic.com/feature/critics-pick-top-10-best-albums-of-2018|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

