2019年2月，凱莉開始了《{{le|流行警报巡迴演唱會|Caution World Tour}}》<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Kelly |first1=Tetris |title=Mariah Carey Kicks Off Caution World Tour With Resplendent Dallas Show: Watch Highlights |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/concerts/8500711/mariah-carey-caution-world-tour-dallas-concert-opening-night |magazine=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]] |access-date=March 20, 2019 |date=March 2019 |archive-date=2019-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715164131/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/concerts/8500711/mariah-carey-caution-world-tour-dallas-concert-opening-night |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳|皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳]]駐留演唱了三天後，《[[衛報|衛報]]》的記者麥可·克雷格（Michael Cragg）描述凱莉“令人難以置信、調皮的表演”是當作她“鍍金的流行女歌星”身份的證明<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/may/26/mariah-carey-review-royal-albert-hall-london|title=Mariah Carey review – gold-plated pop diva cements her legacy|last=Cragg|first=Michael|date=May 26, 2019|newspaper=The Guardian|access-date=June 7, 2019|archive-date=2021-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210803062015/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/may/26/mariah-carey-review-royal-albert-hall-london|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同樣，《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》的凱特·所羅門（Kate Solomon）稱讚這些表演是“超現實但令人愉悅的，且在一位巨星下顯得更閃耀，更有趣”<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/mariah-carey-royal-albert-hall-review-playful-performance-reveals/|title=Mariah Carey, Royal Albert Hall review: playful performance reveals the pop diva's lighter side|last=Solomon|first=Kate|date=May 26, 2019|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|access-date=June 7, 2019|archive-date=2021-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210803062023/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/mariah-carey-royal-albert-hall-review-playful-performance-reveals/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{fact|2019年3月4日，專輯的第二張單曲《{{le|萬萬不可|A No No}}》發行，並在美國R＆B數位歌曲銷售榜達到第17名。}}

2019年5月29日，電影《[[可能還愛你|可能還愛你]]》（靈感來自於凱莉的歌曲《[[永遠的寶貝|永遠的寶貝]]》）在[[Netflix|Netflix]]上發行<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Netflix|title=Always Be My Maybe {{!}} Trailer {{!}} Netflix|date=May 16, 2019|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iHBcWHY9lN4|access-date=May 16, 2019|archive-date=2022-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220114133807/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iHBcWHY9lN4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年8月25日，凱莉與Walkers洋芋片品牌簽下了1200萬美元的合約<ref name="mirror.co.uk">{{Cite web|url=https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/music-megastar-mariah-carey-set-19006237|title=Music megastar Mariah Carey 'set to become the new face of Walkers Crisps'|first=Sam|last=Elliott|date=August 26, 2019|website=mirror|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210929005444/https://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/music-megastar-mariah-carey-set-19006237|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2019年9月18日，凱莉發行了美國電視連續劇《{{le|Mixed-ish|Mixed-ish}}》的主題曲《{{le|In the Mix|In the Mix}}》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8530291/mariah-carey-mixed-ish-theme-song-in-the-mix-music-video|title=Mariah Carey Unveils 'Mixed-Ish' Theme Song, 'In the Mix': Watch the Music Video|date=September 17, 2019|website=Billboard|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211028153137/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8530291/mariah-carey-mixed-ish-theme-song-in-the-mix-music-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{fact|這首歌在美國[[告示牌|告示牌]]R＆B數位歌曲銷售中排名第9，並在匈牙利排名前20。}}

2019年11月1日，凱莉再次發行並慶祝她的假日專輯《[[祝福_(玛丽亚·凯莉专辑)|祝福]]》25週年。25週年專輯中包括原始專輯以及另一張唱片，收錄凱莉 1994年在[[聖若望堂_(帕爾馬)|聖約翰教堂]]舉行的現場表演及《{{tsl|en|Merry Christmas II You||祝你聖誕快樂}}》的幾首曲目；其他曲目包括"Lil Snowman"和"The Star"及混音版本的曲目<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8542005/mariah-carey-christmas-deluxe-album-video-unreleased-footage|title=It's November 1st, and Mariah Carey Has Decided 'It's Time' For Christmas With a Few Early Presents For Fans|date=November 1, 2019|website=Billboard|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211027153156/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8542005/mariah-carey-christmas-deluxe-album-video-unreleased-footage|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年11月2日，Walkers洋芋片品牌發布了凱莉代言的廣告<ref name="mirror.co.uk" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WvuS3Xz_q-8|title=Mariah Carey Walkers commercial 2019 on www.youtube.com|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211129123223/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WvuS3Xz_q-8|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{fact|它因其幽默而受到評論家的稱讚}}。為慶祝25週年《祝福》，她與[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]組織一本禮物指南<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/b?ie=UTF8&node=15684304011|title=Mariah Carey Gift Guide @ Amazon.com|website=www.amazon.com|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210928205928/https://www.amazon.com/b?ie=UTF8&node=15684304011|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也跟[[施華洛世奇|施華洛世奇]]合作推出聖誕飾品<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.swarovski.com/en-US/p-5543287/25th-Anniversary-Holiday-Ornament-by-Mariah-Carey/|title=Mariah Carey bijou 25th Anniversary Holiday Ornament by Mariah Carey on www.swarovski.com}}</ref>。{{fact|2019年11月22日，"聖誕節我只要你"系列巡演在美國展開，到2019年12月15日結束。}}

2019年12月5日，[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]的音樂平台根據她的歌曲“你是我最想要的聖誕禮物”製作並發布了一部迷你紀錄片，於同月稍晚發布<ref>{{Cite magazine|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/mariah-carey-all-i-want-for-christmas-amazon-documentary-921853/|title=Mariah Carey's 'All I Want for Christmas Is You' Gets Its Own Amazon Documentary|last=Shaffer|first=Claire|date=December 4, 2019|magazine=Rolling Stone|access-date=March 9, 2020|archive-date=2021-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105013416/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/mariah-carey-all-i-want-for-christmas-amazon-documentary-921853/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{fact|2019年12月21日，玛丽亚·凯莉第十九支冠軍單曲《[[你是我最想要的聖誕禮物|你是我最想要的聖誕禮物]]》誕生，並蟬聯3周（至2020年1月4日）。除了是[[告示牌|告示牌]]中第二支奪冠的佳節單曲，也是她個人第一支2010年代冠軍單曲，更是釋出後時隔二十五年才奪冠。在告示牌排行榜上也是個人歌手中冠軍週數維持最久的紀錄保持者（十九支單曲共待在冠軍位置八十七週），更是史上第一位擁有的冠軍單曲橫跨四個世代的歌手（在1990年代、2000年代、2010年代及2020年代）。}}

====出道30週年====
2020年1月，作曲家名人堂組織宣佈在6月11日於[[紐約市|紐約市]][[馬奎斯萬豪酒店|馬奎斯萬豪酒店]]的頒獎典禮上，將凱莉入選為作曲家名人堂成員<ref>{{cite web |author1=Joey Nolfi |title=Mariah Carey to be inducted into Songwriters Hall of Fame |url=https://ew.com/awards/2020/01/16/2020-songwriters-hall-of-fame-inductees-mariah-carey/ |website=EW.com |accessdate=2020-08-20 |language=EN |archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116201213/https://ew.com/awards/2020/01/16/2020-songwriters-hall-of-fame-inductees-mariah-carey/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同月，該歌手宣布將於2020年9月29日發行她的回憶錄，題為《The Meaning Of Mariah Carey》<ref>{{cite web |last1=Sodomsky |first1=Sam |title=Mariah Carey Announces Memoir The Meaning of Mariah Carey |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/mariah-carey-announces-memoir-the-meaning-of-mariah-carey/ |website=Pitchfork |accessdate=2020-08-20 |language=en-us |archive-date=2020-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231025831/https://pitchfork.com/news/mariah-carey-announces-memoir-the-meaning-of-mariah-carey/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並透過Pan Macmillan和Henry Holt and Company發行。2020年3月29日，凱莉參加了由[[艾爾頓·約翰|艾爾頓·約翰]]主持的“iHeart Living Room Concert For America”，她演唱了她的熱門單曲[[Always_Be_My_Baby|Always Be My Baby]]。該活動在對抗COVID-19的活動中籌集了超過800萬美元<ref>{{cite news |author1=Jem Aswad |title=Elton John’s ‘Living Room Concert for America’ Raises $8 Million for Coronavirus Relief |url=https://variety.com/2020/music/news/elton-john-living-room-concert-for-america-raises-8-million-coronavirus-1203551388/ |accessdate=2020-08-20 |work=Variety |date=2020-04-01 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308150656/https://variety.com/2020/music/news/elton-john-living-room-concert-for-america-raises-8-million-coronavirus-1203551388/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

7月15日，凱莉宣佈「MC30」企劃，發行一連串未發行單曲，慶祝出道30週年<ref>{{cite news |author1=Rania Aniftos |title=Mariah Carey Shares Incredible Vocal Warm-Up From Her Debut Album Era |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9423530/mariah-carey-vocal-warm-up-debut-album-era |accessdate=2020-08-20 |work=Billboard |date=2020-07-23 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031071358/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9423530/mariah-carey-vocal-warm-up-debut-album-era/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

8月19日，凱莉宣佈於10月2日發行《[[The_Rarities|The Rarities]]》合輯，首張單曲《[[Save_the_Day|Save the Day]]》將於8月21日發行<ref>{{cite news |author1=Chloe Melas |title=Mariah Carey announces new album called 'The Rarities' |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/19/entertainment/mariah-carey-the-rarities-album/index.html |accessdate=2020-08-20 |work=CNN |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110053430/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/08/19/entertainment/mariah-carey-the-rarities-album/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==慈善事业及其他活动==
凱莉是一個參與了很多慈善組織的慈善家。<ref name=fresh>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=c98gAAAAIBAJ&sjid=I2sFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2220,934579&dq=camp+mariah&hl=en|title=Carey a Fresh Face for Fresh Air Fund|last=Hopkins|first=Eugene|work=Sun Journal|date=1994-12-04|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907205833/http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=c98gAAAAIBAJ&sjid=I2sFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2220,934579&dq=camp+mariah&hl=en|archivedate=2013-09-07}}</ref>1990年代初，她成為了一個旨在讓美國紐約內城青年有機會接觸藝術和瞭解職業生涯機遇的夏令營{{tsl|en|The Fresh Air Fund|新鮮空氣基金會|Camp Mariah}}的合夥創辦人。<ref name=fresh/>凱莉因此獲得了国会地平线奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1426935/19990413/carey_mariah.jhtml|title=Mariah Carey to Receive Congressional Award for Charity Efforts|publisher=MTV News|last=Vineyard|first=Jennifer|date=1999-04-13|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110131074113/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1426935/19990413/carey_mariah.jhtml|archivedate=2011-01-31}}</ref>凱莉也將歌曲《[[英雄_(瑪麗亞·凱莉歌曲)|英雄]]》和《[[甜蜜一日|甜蜜一日]]》的版稅所得捐給了慈善機構。<ref name="billboard2">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/472771/mariah-carey-embarrassed-over-gadhafi-linked-concert |title=Mariah Carey 'Embarrassed' Over Gadhafi-Linked Concert |work=Billboard |date=2009-09-14 |accessdate=2012-08-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130330202643/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/472771/mariah-carey-embarrassed-over-gadhafi-linked-concert |archivedate=2013-03-30 }}</ref>此外，她還加入了[[願望成真基金|願望成真基金]]來幫助患有生命威脅疾病的兒童實現願望。2006年11月，她以“極度慷慨與實現眾多願望”的成就被評為“基金會願望偶像”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news-article/carey-packs-times-square-with-early-morning-show|title=Mariah Carey – Carey Packs Times Square With Early Morning Show|publisher=Contactmusic.com|date=2005-04-12|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120822020557/http://www.contactmusic.com/news-article/carey-packs-times-square-with-early-morning-show|archivedate=2012-08-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1654204/mariah-carey-performs-with-mother-on-holiday-tv-special.jhtml|title=Mariah Carey Performs With Mother On Holiday TV Special|last=Dinh|first=James|publisher=MTV News|date=2010-12-12|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623214126/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1654204/mariah-carey-performs-with-mother-on-holiday-tv-special.jhtml|archivedate=2012-06-23}}</ref>2008年，凯莉成为[[世界糧食計劃署|世界糧食計劃署]]的饥荒关怀大使。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/mariah_saves_world_one_chalupa_time/30720|title=Carey Saves the World, One Chalupa At a Time|last=Ryan|first=Joyal|work=E! Online|date=2006-08-29|accessdate=2011-08-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120114112518/http://www.eonline.com/news/mariah_saves_world_one_chalupa_time/30720|archivedate=2012-01-14}}</ref>2010年2月，原本为电影《[[天生不是寶貝|天生不是寶貝]]》发行的歌曲《{{tsl|en|100% (Mariah Carey song)|100% (玛丽亚·凯莉歌曲)|100%}}》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2010/02/mariah-carey-to-release-duet-remix-album.html|title=Mariah Carey Will Release Duet, Remix Album|last=Kennedy|first=Gerrick|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2010-02-26|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68WCdxqby?url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2010/02/mariah-carey-to-release-duet-remix-album.html|archivedate=2012-06-18}}</ref>成为[[2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会]]的主题曲之一，凯莉将歌曲的全部收入都捐给了[[美國奧林匹克委員會|美國奧林匹克委員會]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.att.com/gen/press-room?pid=4800&cdvn=news&newsarticleid=30499|title=AT&T to Produce Exclusive Soundtrack for Athletes Competing in 2010 Olympic Winter Game|publisher=AT&T|date=2010-02-26|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607231728/http://www.att.com/gen/press-room?pid=4800&cdvn=news&newsarticleid=30499|archivedate=2011-06-07}}</ref>

