obe&desc=CAREY%2C+ON!&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-25}}</ref>，高音可達第七個八度<ref>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/orlandosentinel/access/90254402.html?dids=90254402:90254402&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug+28%2C+1990&author=&pub=Orlando+Sentinel&desc=HER+7-OCTAVE+VOICE+FINALLY+GETS+NOTICED&pqatl=google|title=Her 7-Octave Voice Finally Gets Noticed|last=Harris|first=James|work=Orlando Sentinel|date=1990-08-28|accessdate=2011-08-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725040442/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/orlandosentinel/access/90254402.html?dids=90254402:90254402&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug+28%2C+1990&author=&pub=Orlando+Sentinel&desc=HER+7-OCTAVE+VOICE+FINALLY+GETS+NOTICED&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/access/77383942.html?dids=77383942:77383942&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug+12%2C+1990&author=Wayne+Robins&pub=Newsday+(Combined+editions)&desc=Columbia's+New+`Franchise'&pqatl=google|title=Columbia's New 'Franchise'|last=Robins|first=Wayne|work=Newsday|date=1990-08-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725034128/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/newsday/access/77383942.html?dids=77383942%3A77383942&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AFT&type=current&date=Aug+12%2C+1990&author=Wayne+Robins&pub=Newsday+%28Combined+editions%29&desc=Columbia%27s+New+%60Franchise%27&pqatl=google|archivedate=2012-07-25|accessdate=2022-01-16}}</ref>，獲[[健力士世界紀錄|《吉尼斯世界纪录》]]封为“至尊歌者”<ref name="James">{{harvnb|James|1998|p=74}}</ref>。2003年，经过乐迷和粉丝在线投票，她列入MTV和《{{tsl|en|Blender (magazine)||Blender}}》“音乐界22大最伟大之声”排行榜榜首。凯莉对此表示：“它的真正含义是MTV世代的声音。这当然算是巨大的成就，但我觉得我不敢当。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2003/03/31/1048962696862.html|title=Princess Positive is Taking Care of Inner Mariah|last=Oleman|first=Sarah|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|date=2003-04-01|accessdate=2011-08-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816082050/http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2003/03/31/1048962696862.html|archivedate=2011-08-16}}</ref>她还被列入《Cove》杂志“100名杰出流行歌手”榜单的第二位<ref name="100 Outstanding Pop Vocalists">{{cite web|url=http://celebrities-group.popsugar.com/100-Outstanding-Pop-Vocalists-1659579|title=100 Outstanding Pop Vocalists |work=Cove|date=2008-05-24|accessdate=2017-02-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718134206/http://celebrities-group.popsugar.com/100-Outstanding-Pop-Vocalists-1659579|archivedate=2012-07-18}}</ref>。

關於她的{{tsl|en|voice type||声线类型}}，凯莉曾表示自己是[[女低音|女低音]]，但乐评人认为她實質為[[花腔女高音|花腔女高音]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SB&p_theme=sb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB048008F89C5E3&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=Separated At Birth?|last=Hoven|first=Chris|work=The Sacramento Bee|date=2000-10-13|accessdate=2012-08-12|archive-date=2011-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830053302/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=SB&p_theme=sb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB048008F89C5E3&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesunion.com/entertainment/article/New-CDs-558082.php|title=New CDs|work=Times Union|date=2000-10-13|accessdate=2012-08-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013160334/http://www.timesunion.com/entertainment/article/New-CDs-558082.php|archivedate=2013-10-13}}</ref><ref name="books.google.ca">{{Cite book|title=Rock-N-Roll Gold Rush |last=Dean |first= Maury|authorlink= |year= 2003|publisher= Algora Publishing|location= |isbn= 0-87586-207-1|page= 34|url= https://books.google.com/?id=lJS4EArRBwoC&dq=Rock-N-Roll+Gold+Rush+mariah+carey&pg=PA87&lpg=PA87&q=whitney+houston#PPA34,M1}}</ref>。然而，在当代音乐门类下，歌手声线类型由他们唱的[[音乐类型|音乐类型]]决定。目前流行歌领域暂无官方分类法<ref name="Peckham"/>。曾有过将古典乐声线分类法引入其他演唱流派，但这种分类法随着歌手们采取不借助[[麦克风|麦克风]]，用他们的共鸣扩大他或她的声音的方式发声<ref name="Appleman">{{harvnb|Appleman|1986|p=434}}</ref>而具有争议<ref name="Peckham">{{harvnb|Peckham|2005|p=117}}</ref>。

《纽约时报》的{{tsl|en|Jon Pareles||乔恩·帕雷斯}}称凯莉的低音像延伸到“狗哨般的高音”的“浑厚、深沉沙哑的中音”<ref name=nytreview>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1993/12/13/arts/review-pop-venturing-outside-the-studio-mariah-carey-proves-her-mettle.html|title=Review/Pop; Venturing Outside the Studio, Mariah Carey Proves Her Mettle|last=Pareles|first=Jon|work=The New York Times|date=1993-12-13|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110828121401/http://www.nytimes.com/1993/12/13/arts/review-pop-venturing-outside-the-studio-mariah-carey-proves-her-mettle.html|archivedate=2011-08-28}}</ref>。此外，迈入20世纪90年代末期，凯莉开始在她的作品中融入[[气声|气声]]<ref name=charm>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2535321.stm|title=Carey Charm Offensive|last=Levell|first=Tim|publisher=BBC News|date=2002-12-02|accessdate=2011-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120802122234/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/2535321.stm|archivedate=2012-08-02}}</ref>。BBC新闻的蒂姆·雷维尔（{{lang|en|Tim Levell}}）称她的声音像“贴着麦克风的风骚喘息”<ref name=charm/>，而《今日美国》的爱丽莎·加德纳（{{lang|en|Elysa Gardner}}）则写道：“不可能否认她的声线所带来的影响力，她重复喘息声的华丽融合和嘹亮的花腔，被今日年轻的流行和R&B巨星采用<ref name=gold>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/reviews/2002-12-02-charmbracelet_x.htm|title=Carey Sounds Like 'Gold' on 'Charmbracelet'|last=Gardner|first=Elysa|work=USA Today|date=2002-12-22|accessdate=2011-08-03|archive-date=2012-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315005105/http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/reviews/2002-12-02-charmbracelet_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》的萨沙·弗雷-琼斯认为她的[[音色|音色]]蕴含多种色彩，表示：“凯莉的声音几乎每句歌词都有所转变，从冷冰冰的音调突变成颤抖着的咆哮，之后又变成温润的咕咕喘息声。宽广音域让她将旋律从中低音带往花腔女高音的上层音区。<ref name="newyorker"/>凯莉还有着“耳语般的音区”。在采访凯莉时，《娱乐周刊》的罗恩·纪文斯（{{lang|en|Ron Givens}}）如此阐述：“起先她是从中音歌喉不费吹灰之力的翻滚中发出深情的啊哈声。之后她迅速吸一口气，去到高位，声音几乎改变房间中的大气压力。一个粗暴的俯冲，她好像在尖声长叫同时咆哮着<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,317869,00.html|title=Vision of Loveliness|last=Givens|first=Ron|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=1990-08-03|accessdate=2014-08-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140905225359/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,317869,00.html|archivedate=2014-09-05}}</ref>。”她音高感十分让人敬佩<ref name=nytreview />，乔恩·帕雷斯（{{lang|en|John Pareles}}）认为“她能够徘徊于感官的转变中，借助打趣般的自信咆哮着，切分像[[擬聲吟唱|擬聲吟唱]]......音区令人惊讶地精准<ref name=nytreview />。”

==影响力==
