>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YCgEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA260-IA6&dq=mariah+carey+rainbow&hl=en&ei=qyduTabsD8G4tgfdvezwDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CEQQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=mariah%20carey%20rainbow&f=false|title=Mariah Carey 'Rainbow'|last=Linden|first=Amy|work=Vibe|date=1999-12-12|accessdate=2011-03-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130623025306/http://books.google.com/books?id=YCgEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA260-IA6&dq=mariah+carey+rainbow&hl=en&ei=qyduTabsD8G4tgfdvezwDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CEQQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=mariah%20carey%20rainbow&f=false|archivedate=2013-06-23}}</ref>。”碧昂丝认为凯莉的歌唱和她的歌曲《爱的幻影》影响她在“乱跑乱跳”的孩提时代开始练习唱歌，还帮助她追随音乐家生涯<ref name="newyorker">{{Cite news|url=http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2006/04/03/060403crmu_music|title=Mariah Carey's Record-Breaking Career|last=Frere-Jones|first=Sasha|date=2006-04-06|accessdate=2011-11-10|work=The New Yorker|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65iBi88bl?url=http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2006/04/03/060403crmu_music|archivedate=2012-02-25}}</ref>。[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]表示凯莉是她的主要影响之一和偶像<ref name="mtv.com"/>。[[克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉|克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉]]说歌唱职业生涯早期，凯莉是她的重大影响和偶像之一<ref name="vol"/>。《克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉：明星诞生》（{{lang|en|''Christina Aguilera: A star is made''}}）的作者皮尔·多明戈斯（{{lang|en|Pier Dominguez}}）表示，阿奎莱拉说她喜欢听[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮·休斯顿]]，但凯莉对她的歌唱风格影响最大。凯莉精心打造的成年女性形象引发阿奎莱拉的共鸣。对她阿奎莱拉的影响出自两人都是口碑不一的遗留物的事实<ref>{{Cite book|last=Dominguez|first=Pier|year=2003|title=Christina Aguilera: a star is made: the unauthorized biography|url=https://archive.org/details/christinaaguiler0000domi|publisher=Amber Books Publishing|page=[https://archive.org/details/christinaaguiler0000domi/page/134 134]|isbn=0-9702224-5-9}}</ref>。《[[日本時報|日本時報]]》菲利普·布拉索（{{lang|en|Philip Brasor}}）表示凯莉的声线和花腔风格甚至影响到亚洲的歌手。他写道，日本歌手宇多田光“唱出她所听到的，从横膈肌到她能驾驭的那种花腔，她已经成为继玛丽亚·凯莉升华后的美国流行乐领军人物<ref name=hikaru>{{cite web|url=http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/fm20091218a1.html|title=The Naughties Played It Nice|work=The Japan Times|date=2009-12-18|accessdate=2011-11-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605231037/http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/fm20091218a1.html|archivedate=2011-06-05}}</ref>。”在题为《出如玛丽亚的花腔，入则凯莎的爆发》（{{lang|en|"Out With Mariah's Melisma, In With Kesha's Kick"}}）的文章中，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》作家{{tsl|en|David Browne (journalist)|大衛・布朗 (新聞從業員)|大卫·布朗}}探讨曾经在玛丽亚·凯莉和惠特妮·休斯敦的热衷下广泛流传，而且无孔不入的花腔流行乐风格，如何突然失去对现在无处不在的[[自动调谐|自动调谐]]支持。布朗认为：“但始于二十年前，花腔以前所未有的方式接管流行乐。1990年，玛丽亚·凯莉凭借《爱的幻影》出道，两年后，惠特妮·休斯敦版的《我会永远爱你》将小节设置到无比地高，音符比大多数流行乐迷听过的要更响亮、更长、更多节。”布朗进一步补充道：“后来的那一代歌手，包括阿奎莱拉小姐、詹妮弗·休斯敦和碧昂丝，都围绕着花腔建功立业（{{le|布莱恩·麦金纳|Brian McKnight}}和[[泰瑞斯·吉布森|泰瑞斯·吉布森]]等男歌手也沉醉其中，但支配这种模式的还是女性）<ref name="nytimes.com">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/26/arts/music/26browne.html|work=The New York Times|first=David|last=Browne|title=Out With Mariah's Melisma, In With Kesha's Kick|date=2010-08-10|accessdate=2011-11-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ABcqdJYG?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/26/arts/music/26browne.html?_r=2|archivedate=2012-08-25}}</ref>。”

凯莉被誉为将R&B和嘻哈引入主流流行文化，借助她1995年末歌曲的客串表演普及说唱。《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》编辑{{tsl|en|Sasha Frere-Jones||萨沙·弗雷-琼斯}}认为：“将说唱副歌融入梅西·埃丽奥特和碧昂丝等人的旋律中，成了R&B或嘻哈巨星的标准。”年轻的白人流行巨星，包括布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯、潔西卡·辛普森、克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉和[[超級男孩|超級男孩]]都在过去十年花费众多，让流行乐吸收R&B。此外，琼斯总结：“（凯莉）一位女歌手配一位著名男嘻哈MC的想法改变了R&B，并最终延及整个流行乐坛。尽管如今所有人都不受约束地使用这个想法，但《天后再临-解放咪咪》暗示这依旧由凯莉主宰<ref name="newyorker" />。”《{{le|调音器杂志|The Fader}}》编辑贾尼克·马亚德（{{lang|en|Judnick Mayard}}）指出，至于R&B和嘻哈的合作：“这个举动的冠军属于玛丽亚·凯莉。”马亚德表示：“时至今日，{{tsl|en|Ol' Dirty Bastard||ODB}}和玛丽亚也许仍是史上最佳且最随机的嘻哈合作，”指出由于“《[[Fantasy_(瑪麗亞·凱莉歌曲)|Fantasy]]》的录制”，“R&B和嘻哈或许仍是继姐弟<ref name="thefader.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.thefader.com/2011/01/14/suite903-rb-rejected-and-betrayed/ |title=Suite903: R&B, Rejected and Betrayed |publisher=The Fader |last=Mayard |first=Judnick |date=2009-01-04 |accessdate=2011-11-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911150131/http://www.thefader.com/2011/01/14/suite903-rb-rejected-and-betrayed/ |archivedate=2011年9月11日 }}</ref>。”《纽约时报》的卡莱法·桑纳（{{lang|en|Kelefa Sanneh}}）写道：“20世纪90年代中叶，凯莉女士首创一个子门类，有些人称之为暴力情歌二重唱。如今，帅气的流行巨星都期待着跟粗横的说唱歌手合同，但当凯莉小姐与[[武当帮|武当帮]]的{{tsl|en|Ol' Dirty Bastard||肮脏的混蛋}}为1995年热歌《Fantasy (Remix)》组队时，却是个意外和冲击<ref name=autogenerated7>{{cite news |title=The Summer Buzz: Cicadas and Mariah Carey |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2005/08/04/arts/music/04note.html |work=The New York Times |date=2005-08-04 |accessdate=2010-11-05 |last=Sanneh |first=Kalefa |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510132505/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/08/04/arts/music/04note.html |archivedate=2013-05-10 }}</ref>。”除了影响流行文化和音乐，凯莉也是经典圣诞歌曲《[[你是我最想要的聖誕禮物|你是我最想要的聖誕禮物]]》的推手<ref name=scotherlad>{{cite news |url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/comment/guest-commentary/in-praise-of-a-very-mariah-christmas-by-shona-craven-1.1073617 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718043235/http://www.heraldscotland.com/comment/guest-commentary/in-praise-of-a-very-mariah-christmas-by-shona-craven-1.1073617 |archivedate=2012-07-18 |title=In Praise Of ... A Very Mariah Christmas |last=Craven |first=Shona |work=The Herald |date=2010-12-10 |accessdate=2010-12-10}}</ref>。回顾凯莉的职业生涯，《[[纽约客|纽约客]]》的萨沙·弗雷-琼斯认为，“魅力”歌曲是凯莉最伟大的成就之一，称其为“假日歌曲的鲜有现代附属品”<ref name="newyorker"/>。《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》将《你是我最想要的圣诞礼物》列入最伟大摇滚圣诞榜单的第四位，称其为“圣诞标准”<ref name=autogenerated3>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/photos/the-greatest-rock-and-roll-christmas-songs-20101216/mariah-carey-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-0150435|title=The Greatest Rock and Roll Christmas Songs|last=Greene|first=Andy|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2017-02-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120429221505/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/photos/the-greatest-rock-and-roll-christmas-songs-20101216/mariah-carey-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-0150435 |archivedate=2012-04-29 }}</ref>。在评价她的《[[Greatest_Hits|Greatest Hits]]》专辑时，[[PopMatters|PopMatters]]的德文·鲍尔斯（{{lang|en|Devon Powers}}）写道：“她影响了无数的女歌手。32岁时，她已经成了活着的传奇——即便她从不唱过其他的歌<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.popmatters.com/pm/review/careymariah-greatest|title=Mariah Carey: Greatest Hits|last=Powers|first=Devon|work=PopMatters|date=2002-05-08|accessdate=2011-10-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6I9YwmyNZ?url=http://www.popmatters.com/pm/review/careymariah-greatest|archivedate=2013-07-16}}</ref>。”评论凯莉[[悉尼|悉尼]]演唱会时，《{{tsl|en|MTV Australia||MTV澳大利亚}}》的埃利斯·沃特（{{lang|en|Elise Vout}}）写道：“值得你去看的不是惊人的编曲或高端的制作，而是比生命品质、独一无二的声线更伟大的，传奇玛丽亚·凯莉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com.au/news/gig-review-mariah-carey-live-concert-sydney-australia-january-3-2013/|title=The megastar takes the stage in Australia for the first time in 15 years!|last=Vout|first=Elise|publisher=MTV Australia|date=2013-01-04|accessdate=2013-01-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116031229/http://www.mtv.com.au/news/gig-review-mariah-carey-live-concert-sydney-australia-january-3-2013/|archivedate=2013-01-16}}</ref>。”

==私生活==
录制《音乐盒》时，凯莉开始结识湯米·摩托拉。<ref name="shapiro5">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=74}}</ref>1993年6月5日，两人成婚。<ref name="shapiro6">{{harvnb|Shapiro|2001|pp=75}}</ref>1995年《梦游仙境》发售并大获成功后，凯莉开始侧重私生活，在当时酿成了连续不断的麻烦。<ref name="nickson38">{{harvnb|Nickson|1998|p=156}}</ref>专辑创意分歧和摩托拉控制欲的加强，让两人关系开始破裂。<ref name="nickson38"/>1997年5月30日，两人宣布分居，<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20122408,00.html | title=Swan Song|first1= Steve|last1 = Dougherty | first2 = Sue | last2 = Miller|first3=Wayne|last3=Edwards |date= 1997-06-16| work= People | publisher= Time Inc. |accessdate=2017-02-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002425/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20122408,00.html|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref>并最终于2000年12月2日摩托拉再婚时离婚。<ref name=mottola-remarries>{{cite news| url= http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,621423,00.html| title= Music Mogul Marries| first= Stephen M.| last= Silverman| work= People| date= 1997-10-13| accessdate= 2015-11-09| quote= Tommy Mottola ... married his third wife, Mexican soap opera actress Thalia Soldi, in an extravagant, all-star wedding Saturday night [Oct. 11, 1997] at New York's St. Patrick's Cathedral.| deadurl= no| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20150924163957/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,621423,00.html| archivedate= 2015-09-24}}</ref>1998年到2001年，凯莉与{{tsl|en|Luis Miguel||Luis Miguel}}交往三年。<ref name="Luis Miguel Relationship"/>

在[[安地卡岛|安地卡岛]]海岸的一个小岛一同录制《{{le|再见 (玛丽亚·凯莉歌曲)|Bye Bye (Mariah Carey song)|再见}}》的音乐录影带时，卡莉结交了[[尼克·卡农|尼克·卡农]]。<ref name=success>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,354539,00.html|title=Mariah Carey, Nick Cannon Get Wedding Tattoos|last=McKay|first=Hollie|publisher=Fox News Channel|date=2008-04-03|accessdate=2011-08-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101204436/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,354539,00.html|archivedate=2011-11-01}}</ref>2008年4月30日，凯莉和卡农在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]成婚。<ref name=autogenerated12>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1586974/mariah-carey-nick-cannon-wedding-photo-released.jhtml|title=It's Official! Mariah Carey, Nick Cannon Wedding Photo, Comments Are Released|last=Vineyard|first=Jennier|publisher=MTV News|date=2008-04-09|accessdate=2011-05-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110122034018/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1586974/mariah-carey-nick-cannon-wedding-photo-released.jhtml|archivedate=2011-01-22}}</ref>历经九月怀胎，她于2011年[[剖腹产|剖腹产]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Hammel |first=Sara |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20543870,00.html |title=Mariah Carey Tells Rosie O'Donnell: I Lost 70 Lbs. After Twins |website=People.com |date=2014-05-26 |accessdate=2016-09-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824200038/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20543870,00.html |archivedate=2016-08-24 }}</ref>产下一对[[双胞胎|双胞胎]]。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Christianson|first1=Emily|title=Mariah Carey, Nick Cannon debut twins on '20/20'|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/gossip/2011/10/mariah-carey-nick-cannon-debut-twins-on-2020.html|accessdate=2014-09-10|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2011-10-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911012823/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/gossip/2011/10/mariah-carey-nick-cannon-debut-twins-on-2020.html|archivedate=2014-09-11}}</ref>2014年8月，卡农证实两人已分居数月。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://celebrity.yahoo.com/blogs/celeb-news/nick-cannon-confirms-mariah-carey-marriage-trouble--we-are-living-apart-202727771.html | title = Exclusive: Nick Cannon Confirms He and Mariah Carey Are Living Apart | first = Taryn | last = Ryder | date = 2014-08-21 | work = The Insider With Yahoo | publisher = Yahoo Celebrity | accessdate = 2015-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910022444/https://celebrity.yahoo.com/blogs/celeb-news/nick-cannon-confirms-mariah-carey-marriage-trouble--we-are-living-apart-202727771.html | archivedate = 2015-09-10 }}</ref>2014年12月12日，卡农提出离婚诉讼，并最终于2016年离婚。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fisher|first1=Kendall|title=Mariah Carey and Nick Cannon's Divorce Finalized|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/806335/mariah-carey-and-nick-cannon-s-divorce-has-been-finalized|accessdate=2016-11-01|work=E! Online|date=2016-11-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102163133/http://www.eonline.com/news/806335/mariah-carey-and-nick-cannon-s-divorce-has-been-finalized|archivedate=2016-11-02}}</ref>2016年1月21日，澳大利亚亿万富豪{{tsl|en|James Packer||James Packer}}宣布与凯莉订婚，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/731548/mariah-carey-and-james-packer-are-engaged|title=Mariah Carey and James Packer are Engaged|work=E! Online|date=2016-01-21|accessdate=2016-01-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122173239/http://www.eonline.com/news/731548/mariah-carey-and-james-packer-are-engaged|archivedate=2016-01-22}}</ref>但同年10月，有消息指两人已断交。<ref>{{cite web|title=Mariah Carey breaks silence on James Packer split|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/mariah-carey-breaks-silence-on-james-packer-split/|accessdate=2016-12-02|first=Jackie|last=Willis|date=2016-11-24|publisher=CBS News|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202233148/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/mariah-carey-breaks-silence-on-james-packer-split/|archivedate=2016-12-02}}</ref>{{fact|2016年10月，她開始與美國舞蹈編導Bryan Tanaka約會。}}{{fact|在2018年4月，凱莉公開了她與{{tsl|en|bipolar II disorder||第二型躁鬱症}}的鬥爭。據凱莉的說法，她早在2001年被診斷出患有此疾，但一直以來都保密著。最近，她以藥物和療法的形式尋求治療。|time=2021-12-11}}

据Chris Nickson1998年传记记载，凯莉是位积极的[[圣公会|圣公会教徒]]。<ref>Mariah Carey Revisited: The Unauthorized Biography by Chris Nickson</ref>她曾在2006年表示：
{{cquote|我相信我[[重生_(基督教)|重生]]很多次了。我认为我对[[基督教的神|神]]的景仰和关系已经改变。每当缺少祷告的私人时间，我便感受到差异。我虽然是个斗士，却意识到自己不是主宰。神想做的任何事都会发生。我认为我会无尽头地第二次、第三次、第四次、第五次、第六次重生。拜神所赐，我还活着。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Mariah Carey Testifies New Career Success Down to God|url=http://www.christiantoday.com/article/mariah.carey.testifies.new.career.success.down.to.god/7171.htm|magazine=Christianity Today|accessdate=2006-08-24|date=2006-08-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080321102424/http://www.christiantoday.com/article/mariah.carey.testifies.new.career.success.down.to.god/7171.htm|archivedate=2008-03-21}}</ref>}}

