* {{cite news|url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idCATRE69R2ZD20101028|title=Mariah Carey Announces She Is Pregnant|agency=[[路透社|Reuters]]|date=2010-10-28|accessdate=2011-07-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119060451/http://ca.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idCATRE69R2ZD20101028|archivedate=2012-01-19}}
* {{cite news|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/arts/child-diva-mariah-carey-dances-to-her-own-tune/story-e6frg8n6-1225974077690|title='Child' Diva Mariah Carey Dances To Her Own Tune|last=Teeman|first=Tim|work=[[澳洲人報|The Australian]]|date=2010-12-21|accessdate=2011-07-10}}
* {{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/celebrities/mariah-carey/|title=Mariah Carey|last=Levine|first=Nick|work=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]]|date=2009-11-12|accessdate=2011-05-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110424101233/http://www.digitalspy.com/celebrities/mariah-carey/|archivedate=2011-04-24}}</ref><ref name="billboard.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/957957/2020-vision-mariah-marks-milestone|title=20–20 Vision Mariah Marks Milestone|work=Billboard|accessdate=2011-11-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529081051/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/957957/2020-vision-mariah-marks-milestone|archivedate=2013-05-29}}</ref>MTV与《{{tsl|en|Blender (magazine)|Blender (雜誌)|Blender}}》雜誌将凯莉排为2003年倒计时音乐界22大好声音首位。《Cove》杂志亦将其排为“百大杰出流行歌唱家”第2位。<ref name="100 Outstanding Pop Vocalists"/><ref name=billboardbiog>{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=mariah carey|bio=true}}|title=Mariah Carey Biography & Awards |work=Billboard|accessdate=2011-11-10}}</ref>除了演唱外，凯莉也以词曲创作知名。{{tsl|en|Yahoo! Music||Yahoo Music}}编辑傑森·安克尼写道：“人们经常把她和对手惠特尼·休斯敦和席琳·迪翁做比较，但她们两个创作自己歌曲的能力都比不上（凯莉）。”<ref>{{cite web|last=Ankeny|first=Jason|url=http://new.music.yahoo.com/mariah-carey/biography/|title=Biography – Mariah Carey|publisher=Yahoo Music|accessdate=2011-11-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120715001355/http://new.music.yahoo.com/mariah-carey/biography/|archivedate=2012-07-15}}</ref>《告示牌》杂志认为凯莉是美国20世纪90年代最成功的艺人。{{sfn|Shapiro|2001|p=145}}由于凯莉是世界音乐奖认定的“千禧年最畅销的女性流行艺人”与“90年代美国最畅销的女艺人”，在2000年[[世界音樂獎|世界音樂獎]]上，凯莉获得了“传奇奖”。<ref name=billboardbiog/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.montecarloresort.com/awards/00/w00res00.htm |title=Monte Carlo Resort – Awards |publisher=[[世界音樂獎|World Music Awards]] |date=2000-10-15 |accessdate=2010-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030621152238/http://www.montecarloresort.com/awards/00/w00res00.htm |archivedate=2003-06-21 }}</ref>2003年，她以超过1亿全球专辑销量收获了{{tsl|en|Chopard Diamond award|肖帕尔钻石奖|肖帕尔钻石奖}}。<ref name="NME Artists - Mariah Carey">{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey|title=NME Artists – Mariah Carey|work=NME|accessdate=2010-08-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101205025151/http://www.nme.com/artists/mariah-carey|archivedate=2010-12-05}}</ref>此外，[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]以6300万销售单元将凯莉列为20世纪90年代最畅销的女艺人。<ref name="riaa.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?table=tblTopArt |title=Gold and Platinum – Top Selling Artists |publisher=[[美國唱片業協會|Recording Industry Association of America]] |accessdate=2010-08-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070701163039/http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?table=tblTopArt |archivedate=2007-07-01 }}</ref><ref name="Mariah Marks Milestone">{{cite web|url=http://www.mariahcarey.com/news/news.php?uid=2882|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603190054/http://www.mariahcarey.com/news/news.php?uid=2882|archivedate=2010-06-03|title=Mariah Marks Milestone|publisher=MariahCarey.com|accessdate=2010-05-29}}</ref>在日本，凯莉拥有四张有史以来销量最高的非亚洲艺人发布之专辑。<ref>{{cite web|title=Carey's Ubiquitous Japanese Success|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7g4EAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA1&pg=PA68#v=onepage&q&f=false|work=Billboard|date=1996-01-26|accessdate=2011-11-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622111017/http://books.google.com/books?id=7g4EAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA1&pg=PA68#v=onepage&q&f=false|archivedate=2013-06-22}}</ref>

凯莉排在《告示牌》百强单曲榜全时段最佳艺人榜第5名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/greatest-hot-100-artists|title=Billboard Greatest of All Time Hot 100 Artists|work=Billboard|accessdate=2015-11-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122034612/http://www.billboard.com/charts/greatest-hot-100-artists|archivedate=2015-11-22}}</ref>她在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百强单曲榜]]取得了87周夺冠周数，创下了美国榜单历史之最。<ref name="billboard1">{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=mariah carey|chart=all}} |title=The Emancipation of Mimi – Mariah Carey |work=Billboard|accessdate=2011-11-10}}</ref>在该榜单上，她拥有19首冠军单曲，是拥有冠军单曲数最多的独唱艺人。<ref name="告示牌"/><ref name="Hiscock">{{Cite news|last=Hiscock|first=John|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/6771071/Mariah-Carey-interview-for-Precious.html|title=Mariah Carey Interview for Precious|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2009-12-10|accessdate=2011-11-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110129222224/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/6771071/Mariah-Carey-interview-for-Precious.html|archivedate=2011-01-29}}</ref>凯莉在百强单曲榜上亦拥有3首空降冠军单曲，包括《[[Fantasy_(瑪麗亞·凱莉歌曲)|Fantasy]]》、《[[甜蜜一日|甜蜜一日]]》和《[[甜蜜蜜_(瑪麗亞·凱莉歌曲)|甜蜜蜜]]》，曾是史上拥有空降冠单最多的艺人，此紀錄直到2020年才被[[雅瑞安娜·格蘭德|雅瑞安娜·格蘭德]]超過。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/slideshow/457789?decorator=slideshow&confirm=true |title=Billboard Hot 100 No. 1 Debuts |work=Billboard |accessdate=2010-10-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203144021/http://www.billboard.com/slideshow/457789?decorator=slideshow&confirm=true |archivedate=2010-12-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/photos/426225/billboard-hot-100-no-1-song-debuts/23 |title=Hot 100 No. 1 Debuts: Complete List |work=Billboard |date= |accessdate=2016-09-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915184653/http://www.billboard.com/photos/426225/billboard-hot-100-no-1-song-debuts/23 |archivedate=2016-09-15 }}</ref>其中《Fantasy》的空降更让她成为了美国第一个拥有空降冠单的女艺人。<ref name=billboardbiog/>1994年，凯莉发行了她的首张假日专辑《[[圣诞快乐_(玛丽亚·凯莉专辑)|Merry Christmas]]》，这张专辑全球销量超过1600万，是美国历史上{{tsl|en|best-selling Christmas/holiday albums in the United States|美国畅销假日专辑|最畅销的假日专辑}}。<ref name="mimisales2"/><ref name="national"/><ref name=sasha>{{cite news|url=http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2006/04/03/060403crmu_music|title=On Top: Mariah Carey's Record-Breaking Career|last=Frere-Jones|first=Sasha|work=The New Yorker|date=2006-04-03|accessdate=2010-12-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65iBi88bl?url=http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2006/04/03/060403crmu_music|archivedate=2012-02-25}}</ref><ref name=independent>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/old-chestnuts-roasting-ghosts-of-christmas-music-past-764334.html|title=Old Chestnuts Roasting: Ghosts of Christmas Music Past|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|date=2007-12-11|accessdate=2010-12-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111222182557/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/old-chestnuts-roasting-ghosts-of-christmas-music-past-764334.html|archivedate=2011-12-22}}</ref>专辑的歌曲《[[你是我最想要的聖誕禮物|你是我最想要的聖誕禮物]]》是美国唯一一首认证达到多白金的假日歌曲和[[手機鈴聲|手機鈴聲]]。<ref>{{cite news|agency=PR Newswire |url=http://www.thestreet.com/story/10648016/mariah-careys-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-is-worlds-first-double-platinum-holiday-ringtone.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112143110/http://www.thestreet.com/story/10648016/mariah-careys-all-i-want-for-christmas-is-you-is-worlds-first-double-platinum-holiday-ringtone.html |archivedate=2012-01-12 |title=Mariah Carey's 'All I Want For Christmas Is You' Is World's First Double Platinum Holiday Ringtone |publisher=TheStreet |date=2009-12-17 |accessdate=2010-06-29}}</ref>在日本，《獨一無二-白金冠軍單曲全選》销量超过3,800,000，跻身[[日本最暢銷專輯列表|日本最暢銷專輯]]之列。<ref name="Mariah Carey #1's">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=yg0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA49&dq=bodyguard+top+foreign+album&cd=5#v=onepage&q=bodyguard%20top%20foreign%20album&f=false|title='#1's'|work=Billboard|date=1999-01-23|accessdate=2011-11-11}}</ref>在凯莉以《祝福》在亚洲大获成功之后，《告示牌》将凯莉评为在日本唱片最畅销的国际艺人。<ref name="Lichtman">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=aggEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA136&dq=mariah+carey+merry+christmas+debut#v=onepage&q=mariah%20carey%20merry%20christmas%20debut&f=false|title=Mariah Hits Big n Japan|last=Lichtman|first=Irv|work=Billboard|date=1994-11-26|accessdate=2011-11-11}}</ref>凯莉与[[大人小孩雙拍檔|大人小孩雙拍檔]]合作演绎的歌曲《[[甜蜜一日|甜蜜一日]]》在百强单曲榜夺冠16周，是{{tsl|en|List of Billboard Hot 100 chart achievements and milestones|公告牌百强单曲榜成就与里程碑列表|在該榜單奪冠周數第二長的歌曲}}。<ref name="billboard.com"/>2008年，《告示牌》将《我要我們在一起》列为全时段单曲榜第9名。<ref name=autogenerated8>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/specials/hot100/charts/top100-titles-10.shtml|title=The Billboard Hot 100 All-Time Top Songs (10-01) |work=Billboard |date=2010-08-15 |accessdate=2010-08-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100801081615/http://www.billboard.com/specials/hot100/charts/top100-titles-10.shtml |archivedate=2010-08-01}}</ref>这首歌曲还是《告示牌》评出的20世纪第一个十年最流行的歌曲。<ref name=decade/>2009年，凯莉翻唱了{{tsl|en|Foreigner (band)|外国人 (乐队)|外国人乐队}}的单曲《{{tsl|en|I Want to Know What Love Is|我想知道愛}}》，打破了巴西流媒体播放记录，在{{tsl|en|Brasil Hot 100 Airplay|巴西百强流媒体榜}}夺冠27周，是该榜单夺冠周数最多的歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mariahcarey.com/news/news.php?uid=2852|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111107172046/http://mariahcarey.com/news/news.php?uid=2852|archivedate=2011-11-07 |title=Mariah Makes Brazilian Chart History|publisher=Mariahcarey.com|accessdate=2011-11-11}}</ref>2010年，《告示牌》将凯莉列为“25年以来50强节奏布鲁斯与嘻哈艺人”第4名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/950681/the-top-50-rb-hip-hop-artists-of-the-past-25-years|title=The Top 50 R&B / Hip-Hop Artists of the Past 25 Years|work=Billboard|date=2010-11-10|accessdate=2011-11-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130220112631/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/950681/the-top-50-rb-hip-hop-artists-of-the-past-25-years|archivedate=2013-02-20}}</ref>2012年，凯莉在[[VH1|VH1]]评选的「音樂領域百大傑出女性」排行第3。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2012-02-13/vh1s-100-greatest-women-in-music-complete-list/|title=100 Greatest Women in Music|publisher=[[VH1|VH1]]|accessdate=2017-02-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130402201858/http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2012-02-13/vh1s-100-greatest-women-in-music-complete-list/|archivedate=2013-04-02}}</ref>2015年8月6日，凯莉是第2556位在[[好萊塢星光大道|好萊塢星光大道]]上，有了一颗属于自己的星星。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Leopold|first1=Todd|title=Mariah Carey may join 'Empire,' gets Walk of Fame star|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/08/06/entertainment/mariah-carey-hollywood-star-empire-feat/|accessdate=2015-08-07|publisher=CNN|date=2015-08-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150809064516/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/08/06/entertainment/mariah-carey-hollywood-star-empire-feat|archivedate=2015-08-09}}</ref>{{fact|2017年，[[PETA|PETA]]授予她“動物天使獎”，以紀念她在動畫電影《{{tsl|en|All I Want For Christmas Is You (film)|聖誕節我只要你}}》致力於描述著一位女孩收養流浪狗的故事。}}

{{fact|2019年10月，凱莉與[[Jennifer_Anisto|Jennifer Anisto]]、[[Awkwafina|Awkwafina]]、[[Brie_Larson|Brie Larson]]、[[Chaka_Khan|Chaka Khan]]和[[Dana_Walden|Dana Walden]]一起被《[[綜藝|綜藝]]》雜誌評選為"權力的女性"。2019年11月24日，《你是我最想要的聖誕禮物》獲得了[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]的三項紀錄，分別是"最暢銷知名的聖誕節歌曲之一"、"24小時內在[[Spotify|Spotify]]上串流播放次數最多的歌曲（女性）（在2018年12月的24小時之內達到10,819,009個串流播放次數）"、"在[[英國單曲榜|英國單曲榜]]位居前十名最多周的聖誕歌曲（20周）"。}}

